Okubunda kw'obulwadde bwa coronavirus (COVID-19) okwongera mu EU/Ebitundu bya Bulaaya n'obw Bungereza, 1 Jjanwali okutuuka 15 Maaki 2020
Embeera y'obulwadde bwa coronavirus (COVID-19) eyongedde okusaasaana mu mawanga g'omu Bulaaya/Emirimu gya Bulaaya n'obwakabaka bwa Bungereza nga kikakasa nti wadde nga buli ggwanga lyawukana ku mutendera gwalyo, ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kyeyongedde mu bwangu mu mawanga gonna.
Okusinziira ku byatuuka mu Italy, ensi, amalwaliro, n'ebitongole ebirunda abalwadde ab'amaanyi balina okwongera okwetegekera okulwanyisa obulwadde bwa COVID-19 obunaaba bujja okwetaagisa obujjanjabi, naddala mu bitongole ebirunda abalwadde ab'amaanyi.
Nga 31 Ddesemba 2019, akawuka ka Pneumonia akali mu kkuuma etamanyiddwa butereevu kaalabika mu Wuhan, Hubei Province, China.
Ku 9 Jjanwali 2020, Ekitongole eky'Okukebera n'Okunonyereza ku Bulwadde mu China kyagamba nti ekirwadde kino kyava ku kawuka ka coronavirus kati akayitibwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Okuva olwo, obulwadde obwaleetebwa obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 buyitibwa coronavirus (COVID-19).
Obujulizi obuliwo bukakasa nti abantu nga 80 ku buli kikumi abalina COVID-19 balwala obulwadde obw'omutawaana, ekitegeeza nti balina obulwadde bw'omukka obulimu oba obutaliimu pneumonia, era abasinga obungi ku bano bawona.
Mu bantu 14 ku buli kikumi, COVID-19 yeeyongera okuba ey'amaanyi era nga yeetaaga okujjanjabibwa mu ddwaliro, ate abalala 6 ku buli kikumi balwala nnyo era nga beetaaga okujjanjabibwa mu ddwaliro.
Omutindo gw'abantu abafa nga bali mu ddwaliro olw'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 guli ku 4%.
Mu kunoonyereza, twekenneenye enkola y'ebyenjigiriza y'obubenje bw'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu mawanga ga European Union/Economic Area (EU/EEA) ne United Kingdom (UK) ne tugigeraageranya n'ebyo ebyali mu Ssaza ly'e Hubei, China.
Twakola n'okugeraageranya omuwendo gw'abantu abafunye COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK n'ogw'abantu abafunye COVID-19 mu Italy mu 31 Jjanwali okutuuka 15 Masse 2020.
Embeera ya COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK
Oluvannyuma lwa China, COVID-19 esangibwa mu bitundu ebirala eby'ensi era n'ebikolwa by'ekirwadde kino mu nsi yonna bigoberedde ebyo ebiri mu China.
Nga 11, March 2020, dayirekita w'ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO) yalangirira COVID-19 nga kawumpuli.
Mu Eurosurveillance 2020 eya March 5, Spiteri et al. baategeezezza ku muntu asoose mu Bulaaya okuba nti alina ekikonge kya COVID-19 okusinziira ku njawulo ya WHO.
Mu EU/EEA, abantu abasatu abaasooka okukakasiddwa nti balina obulwadde buno baabuulirwa France nga 24 Jjanwali 2020 mu bantu abaakomawo okuva e Wuhan, Hubei mu China.
Nga 15 Ogwokusatu 2020, COVID-19 yazuulibwa mu nsi 30 eza EU/EEA ne Bungereza (UK), wakati wa 31 December 2019 ne 15 March 2020 nga n'olunaku olwo mwekwataganyizibwa, waaliwo abantu 39,768 abazuulibwa nga balina COVID-19 era 1,727 be baafa, nga 17,750 be baafa ate 1,441 be baafa mu Italy yokka.
Okufuna omuwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa nga balina COVID-19
Mu European Centers for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC), omuwendo gw'abantu abaakazuulibwa nga balina COVID-19 buli lunaku gukyusibwa ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'oku makya. Omuwendo guno gukubirwa mu bitongole by'eby'obulamu eby'ensi ez'enjawulo, ebitongole by'ebyobulamu eby'ensi yonna n'ebya disitulikiti, ne WHO.
Ebizuuliddwa byakozesebwa mu kwekenneenya embeera ya COVID-19 mu EU/EEA ne UK, n'okugeraageranya n'embeera eri mu Italy.
Ng'ekigera ky'abasajja abalina COVID-19 ekirimu, tubalirira abantu abafa mu nnaku 14 ez'emabega, nga kino kitwaliramu n'ebikolwa ebyenjawulo eby'omu butonde mu buli ggwanga mu EU/EEA ne UK, mu kiseera okuva nga 1 Jjanwali okutuuka nga 15 omwezi gw'Okusatu, 2020.
Ate era, tubala ebifo by'abantu abazuuliddwa mu buli ggwanga nga 15 Maaki 2020 ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'oku makya nga bifaananamu n'eby'abantu abazuuliddwa mu Italy mu kiseera kya 31 omwezi/omwezi ogusooka n'okutuusa 15 omwezi ogw'okusatu 2020.
Embeera ya COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK
Embeera y'ebyafaayo ebikubibwa mu nnaku 14 ez'edda mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK zitera okugoberera embeera y'omu Hubei (China) (Ekifaananyi 1).
Ku EU/EEA ne UK okutwalira awamu, obulwadde bwa COVID-19 bwatandika okwetoloola nga 21 Febwali, n'okweyongera ennyo nga 28 Febwali 2020 (Ebyongerezeddwako).
Enkula eno esimbiddwa nnyo ku kweyongera kw'omuwendo gw'abalwadde abavudde mu Italy, naye amawanga amalala gonna agali mu EU/EEA ne Bungereza balaze okwongera kw'omuwendo gw'abantu abafunye COVID-19 (Okunoonyereza).
Ekifaananyi 2 kiraga omuwendo gw'abantu abafunye obulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK nga bwegugeraageranyizibwa n'omuwendo gw'abantu abafunye obulwadde mu Italy mu kiseera eky'omwaka 31 January-15 March 2020.
Ebyafaayo biraga nti, nga 15 Ogwokusatu ssaawa 8:00 ez'ekiro, amawanga amalala 15 aga EU/EEA ne UK baali baakafuna omuwendo gw'abalwadde ogwenkanankana n'ogw'e Italy mu wiiki ssatu ezaali emabega oba wansi.
Ebyava mu kunoonyereza kwaffe biraga nti omuwendo gw'abantu abalagibwa obulwadde bwa COVID-19 gweyongera mu EU/EEA ne UK.
Enkola eyalabwa ku nkula y'abantu abalina COVID-19 eraga nti ekirwadde kino kigenda mu maaso mu nsi zonna mu ngeri y'emu.
Kino tekisinziira ku butali bumu obuli mu nsi, enjawulo mu bujjanjabi bw'abantu, n'enjawulo mu ngeri gye bategeeramu abantu mu nsi yonna, n'enjawulo mu nkola ez'okulonda abalwadde okukeberebwa okukakasa nti balina COVID-19, nga mw'otwalidde n'okugezesebwa okw'oluvannyuma.
Mu ntandikwa ya Maaki 2020, abasawo mu bitundu bya Italy ebikoseddwa baayogera ku mbeera eya 10% ey'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abaali beetaaga okujjanjabwa ennyo era ensonda mu mawulire zaategeeza nti amalwaliro n'ebifo ebirimu abalwadde ab'amaanyi mu bitundu ebyo byali bituuse ku ntikko y'amaanyi gaabyo.
Mu kiseera kino, ebiwandiiko by'abantu abajjanjabibwa mu malwaliro n'ebitundu by'abalina obulwadde obwa COVID-19 ku ddaala lya EU/EAA biyinza okufunibwa ku bantu 6% n'abantu 1% bokka (ebiwandiiko tebirabiddwa).
Wabula, obubaka bulina okukuŋŋaanyizibwa mu ngeri entegeke obulungi okusobola okugattibwako obubaka obuli mu kulabirira obulwadde buno obwesigamye ku muwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa n'abafa.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu 2010-2011 kwalaga enjawulo ey'amaanyi mu kutereka ebitanda eby'okulabirira mu ddwaliro eryabujjanjabi mu Bulaaya, okuva ku 29.2 mu Bugirimaani okutuuka ku 4.2 buli bantu 100,000 mu Portugal.
Kino kitegeeza nti ensi eziyinza okuba n'ebikozesebwa bingi oba bitono okusinga Italy (12,5 ebitanda mu ddwaaliro ly'amaanyi n'ebikozesebwa mu ddwaaliro ly'ekisawo ku bantu 100,000 mu 2010-2011).
Embeera ey'okugezesa ekwata ku bujjanjabi obujjuvu, nga kubalirira omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga mu EU/EEA ne UK nga ku 90% nga bali mu mbeera ey'obutaba na buliri mu buliri obwavu, bawadde mu kukyusa okw'omukaaga okw'ebitongole ebirwanyisa ekirwadde kya COVID-19.
Olw'okuba nti ebirwadde bino by'ekika ekimu mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK, era n'ebirwadde n'ebitundu by'ab'obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi by'ebiseera ebisinga bitera okuweereza abantu abali mu bitundu eby'enjawulo, obubaka obukwata ku birwadde n'ebitundu by'obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi businga okuweebwa mu ddaala ya NUTS-2.
Ebyafaayo okuva mu Italy n'embeera eriwo mu nsi endala biraga nti ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kikula mangu mu EU/EEA ne UK.
N'olwekyo, ensi, amalwaliro n'ebitongole ebirunda abalwadde mu ddwaaliro eriyitibwa ICU birina okwetegekera embeera y'okusaasaanya SARS-CoV-2 mu bantu n'okweyongera kw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abeetaaga obujjanjabi, naddala obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi, nga bwe kibadde mu bitundu ebiruddeko mu Italy.
Nga bwe kyalagibwa mu kuddamu okw'ebiseera ebiyise mu kukyusa obubenje mu ECDC, kikulu nnyo okubaako n'obumalirivu mu ngeri yonna okusobola okukendeeza okusaasaana kwa SARS-CoV-2, nga tukozesa enkola ey'okusiba obubenje mu ngeri y'okukendeeza obubenje, kubanga omuwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa mu bwangu, nga bwe kyasuubirwa, kiyinza okufiiriza abasawo n'abo abakola ku by'okulabirira abalwadde okutegeera, okukkiriza, n'okutereeza engeri entuufu ey'okuddamu singa tebatera kukolera bwe batyo.
Okweekenneenya okw'amangu okw'obulabe era kwassaawo enkola z'obulamu bw'abantu ez'okweggyamu akabi akali mu bulwadde.
Waliwo omukisa omutono ng'amawanga galina okwongera amaanyi mu kufuba okuziyiza okusaasaana kwa SARS-CoV-2 n'okuggyawo obuzibu ku bujjanjabi.
Singa kino kilemererwa, ebitundu ebirala eby'amawanga ga EU/EEA biyinza okufuna abalwadde abetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi mu nnaku oba wiiki ezijja.
Omulwadde wa coronavirus ow'omwaka 2019 (COVID-19), ey'ekika kya coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kati yafiiriddemu abantu abasoba mu 3,000 era n'awonya abantu abasoba mu 80,000 mu China n'awalala mu nsi yonna, nga kino kivuddeko akatyabaga mu bantu.
Okufaananako akawuka akaawukana ku ka SARS-CoV, akaaleeta Sars mu nkumi n'enkumi z'abantu mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 eyinza okuba nga nayo eyatandika n'ennyonyi era n'eyinza okuba nga nayo yaleeta obubonero obufaanana mu ngeri y'emu.
Wadde kiri kityo, COVID-19 erina obulwadde obutonotono n'obutafa nnyo okusinga SARS, naye ekwata nnyo abantu abakulu n'abasajja okusinga abakazi.
Mu kwanukula ku muwendo gw'ebitabo ebyeyongedde ku bulwadde buno obugenda obujja, ekitundu kino kigezaako okuwaayo ekyewuunyisa ku nsonga eno ey'okunoonyereza okw'amangu.
Tujja kwogera ku misingi gy'obwannannyini, obuzaale, obuzaale, okuzuula, obujjanjabi, n'okwewala endwadde.
Wadde nga wakyaliwo ebibuuzo bingi ebikyaliwo ebitazze kuddibwamu, tusuubira nti okunoonyereza kuno kujja kuyamba mu kutegeera n'okuggyawo endwadde eno ey'akabi.
Embaga y'Obuggulo nga January 25, 2020 yafuuka ekijjukizo ekitabangawo era ekitayinza kwerabirwa eri abantu bonna ab'omu China abalagirwa okusigala awaka mu kiseera ky'oluwummula n'oluvannyuma lwa wiiki eziddako olw'ekirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe.
Akawuka kano kakwatagana nnyo ne koonavayiira (CoV) eyaviirako ekirwadde kya siriimu (SARS) mu 2003; olwa kino, akawuka kano kaweebwa erinnya SARS-CoV-2 ekibiina ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO) nga February 11, 2020, era ekirwadde kye kivaako kiyitibwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Obulwadde bwatandikira mu kibuga Wuhan mu China, era ne busaasaana mu ggwanga lyonna era ne mu nsi endala kumpi 50 okwetooloola ensi yonna.
Omwaka guno gwayitawo nga March 2, 2020 era nga abantu 80,000 bebakakasiddwa nti balina obulwadde bwa COVID-19, nga abasukka mu 40,000 bebakasumululwa okuva mu nsi zaabwe ate abalala 3,000 bebakafa.
WHO erabula nti COVID-19 ye 'mulabe w'abantu omukulu' era nti asobola okuba n'obulabe bungi okusinga ebikolwa bya bannalukalala.
Okusinziira ku PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu myezi ebiri gyokka okuva ku lipoota esooka eya 7 Jjanwali 2020 ey'okunoonyereza ku ngeri obuwuka gye bwawandikibwa okuva mu balwadde, empapula ezisukka mu 200 ze zaakubibwa ku COVID-19, nga zikwata ku by'obusaayi, endwadde, ekireetera, n'engeri y'okujjanjaba.
Okunoonyereza kuno kugezezzaako okukkaatiriza enkulaakulana mu kunoonyereza ku nsonga eno empya era egenda okulaakulana amangu.
Nga bwe kisoboka, tujja kugezaako okugeraageranya COVID-19 ku SARS n'endwadde endala eziva ku CoV, ekiyitibwa Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS, ekyayaka mu 2012).
Tujja kwogera ku ebyo bye tuyize ku bulwadde n'ebibuuzo ebirala ebikulu.
Okusinziira ku mpisa, CoVs zitwalibwa okuba nga za ssenyiga wa bantu, naddala ezireeta ebinyeebwa ebitundu 15 ku buli kikumi 4.
Kyokka, mu kyasa kino, tulabye emirundi ebiri obuwuka obuleeta obulwadde bw'abantu obunene ennyo, SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV, nga buli emu yaviirako obulwadde obwasooka mu China mu 2003 ne mu Saudi Arabia mu 2012, era oluvannyuma ne busaasaana mu nsi endala nnyingi nga bwavaamu endwadde ez'amaanyi n'abafu.
N'olwekyo, COVID-19 y'emu ku ntalo z'akawuka ka CoV esatu mu byafaayo by'omuntu.
Nga bwe kiragiddwa mu Kifaananyi 1.1, ekibinja ky'obulwadde bw'obusawo obutamanyiddwa ensibuko kyakasookera ddala okusabibwa okuva mu Wuhan nga 31, December 2019 eri akakiiko k'ebyobulamu aka National Health Commission of the People's Republic of China.
Oluvannyuma lw'ennaku musanvu, ekirwadde kya CoV kyateekebwawo.
Ku 15 January 2020, omulwadde eyasooka okuva mu Wuhan yalagibwa.
Mu kiseera kye kimu, obulwadde bwasaasaana mangu mu bibuga, mu matwale, ne mu mawanga amalala.
Nga 20 January, ekirwadde kyalabisibwa eri abasawo, ekiraga nti ekirwadde kino kisobola okusaasaana okuva ku muntu omulala.
Nga 23 omwezi ogwa Janwali, ekitundu kya Wuhan kyateekebwako akawayiro era entambula y'abantu bonna yakoma.
Nga 24 omwezi ogusooka, okunoonyereza okwasooka ku bulwadde kuno kwalaga nti ku balwadde 41 abakakasiddwa nti balina obulwadde buno, 21 bokka be baatuukirira butereevu akatale k'ebigulumiza mu Wuhan, ekyetwalibwa okuba nga we kaaso kaasoose okuva mu nsolo ezitamanyiddwa.
Nga 30 omwezi ogusooka, WHO yalangirira nti ekirwadde kino kyali kifuuse ekizibu eky'amaanyi ennyo mu nsi yonna.
Mu kiseera kino, obulwadde buno bubunye mu China yonna ne mu nsi endala 50 okwetooloola ensi (Lub. 2).
Olw'embeera eyeeyongedde mu bwangu, enkomerero y'obulwadde buno n'obunene bwabwo bikyagenda kuddamu okuteekebwa mu nkola.
Ku nga 11 February 2020, okunoonyereza ku multivalenteri ku balwadde 8,866, nga kuliko abalwadde ba COVID-19 4,021 abakakasiddwa, kulaga ekifaananyi ekisingayo obulungi ku bulwadde buno (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 ekwata abantu mu buli myaka, naye okusingira ddala wakati w'emyaka 30-65.
Kumpi ekitundu (47.7%) eky'abantu abafunye obulwadde buno balina emyaka egisukka mu 50, batono nnyo abali wansi w'emyaka 20 era 14 bokka abali wansi w'emyaka 10.
