Mu kiseera eky'okuwandiika okwetegereza kuno, tewali ddagala lya antiviral eryalambikibwa.
Kyokka, okugaba remdesivir mu nnyindo, ekirimu ekirungo kya nucleotide, kyazuulibwa nti kya muganyulo ku mulwadde wa COVID-19 okuva mu Amerika.
Remdesivir eddagala eriggya erirwanyisa endwadde eryavumbulwa Gilead, eryajjanjabirwanga endwadde eziva ku ndwadde nga Ebola ne Marlburg.
Mu kiseera kino, remdesivir era yalaga nti erina obuzibu ku buwuka obulala obwa single-strand RNA, nga mw'otwalidde ne MERS ne SARS.
Okusinziira ku kino, Gilead yawadde China ekirungo kino okukola enkung'aana z'okugezesa ku bantu abalina akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2, era ebivuddemu byali byasuubirwa.
Mu ngeri y'emu, baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir, ne ribavirin byalagirwako ng'ebimu ku biyinza okukozesebwa mu balwadde abalina obuzibu bw'okussa.
Obulwadde bwa mukenenya, obusujja, okugaaya, okwonoona ekibumba, n'ebirala biyinza okubaawo oluvannyuma lw'okujjanjaba nga mukwataganyizibwa n'eddagala lya lopinavir/ritonavir.
Enkolagana y'eddagala lino n'eddagala eddala lyonna omulwadde ly'akozesa erina okwetegereza ennyo.
Omusaayi gw'omulwadde eyawonye era n'okukola ku byuma ebiziyiza endwadde
Waliwo ebyafaayo bingi eby'okufuna omusaayi okuva mu balwadde abawonye endwadde ez'akabi okusobola okujjanjaba abalwadde abalala abalina endwadde y'akabi oba okutangira abantu abalina obulamu obulungi okukwatibwa endwadde eyo.
Mu butuufu, abalwadde abawonawo emirundi mingi baba n'omuwendo gwa antibody ogusinga obungi mu musaayi gwabwe.
Obulwadde bw'omubiri (antibody) ye immunoglobulin (Ig) ey'omu B-lymphocyte erwanyisa obuwuka n'ebirala ebitafa mu mubiri, era esobola okumanya molekulo ez'enjawulo ez'ekiwuka ekyo, n'okuziyiza.
Okusinziira ku kino, plasma yakuŋŋaanyizibwa okuva mu musaayi gw'omugulu gw'abalwadde abaawona COVID-19 era ne gukozesebwa ku balwadde 10 abaali balwadde ennyo.
Obubonero bwabwe bwagenda bukendeera mu ssaawa 24 ng'obulwadde bugaanye, nga n'obutalwadde bweyongedde ate nga n'omusaayi gwongedde.
Kyokka, waliwo okwekenneenya n'okunnyonnyola okwetaagisa okusobola okuteeka enkola eyo mu nkola ey'okukozesa mu ngeri ey'enjawulo nga tebannatandika kukola ddagala lya ddagala.
Ate era, ng'oggyeko obujjanjabi, waliwo obunafu obutali bumu obuzingirwa mu kukozesa plasma.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, obuwuka obuleeta obulwadde busobola okukyusa obukuusa bw'omubiri ne butereetera omuntu okufuna obulwadde obuyitibwa cytokine release syndrome, obuyinza okuba obw'obulabe eri obulamu.
Obungi bw'ebirwadde by'omusaayi butono era plasma nnyingi ze zeetaagisa okujjanjaba abalwadde ennyo.
Okukola n'okufulumya eddagala erirwanyisa endwadde eziriwo mu nsi yonna mu bwangu, kizibu.
N'olwekyo, kikulu nnyo era kyangu okwawula obutofaali bw'omusaayi bwa B okuva mu balwadde abawonye era n'okuzuula ekika ky'ensolo ekirimu eddagala erigema obulwadde oba erirwanyisa obulwadde obwo.
Mu ngeri eno, tusobola okwongera ku muwendo gw'ensimbi ezikozesebwa mu kukola eddagala.
TCM ekozeseddwa okujjanjaba endwadde ez'enjawulo mu China okumala enkumi n'enkumi z'emyaka.
Kyokka, obuvumu bw'omusawo bwesigamye ku ngeri ebitundu by'omusawo gye bikwataganamu, era nga kino kisinziira ku ngeri obulwadde gye bujjamu okusinziira ku ndowooza ya TCM.
Ebintu ebisinga obungi ebikola obulungi tebimanyiddwa oba tebitegeerekeka kubanga kizibu okubikebera oba okubikakasa oba n'ebifaanana.
Mu kiseera kino, olw'okuba tewabaddewo bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19 obwesigika, TCM y'emu ku nzijanjaba endala ez'omugaso eri abalwadde abalina obubonero obutali bwa maanyi oba abo abalwadde ennyo.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, kapsula ya Shu Feng Jie Du ne kapsule ya Lian Hua Qing Wen zaalagibwa okuba ez'omuganyulo mu bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19.
Emisango egisinga kujjira mu basawo ba COVID-19 mu bitundu bya China ebikozesa TCM ku 87% ku balwadde, omuli Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%), ne Hunan (50%), ate mu bitundu bya Hubei, ebikozesa TCM ku 30% ku balwadde ba COVID-19, gye misango egisinga obutono (13%).
Kyokka, okugeraageranya kuno tekuli ku mulembe kubanga waliwo ebintu ebirala ebikulu ebiyinza okuzingirwamu, gamba ng'omuwendo gw'abalwadde n'obuzito bwabwe, ebirina okubalirirwa mu kubalirira kuno.
Nga February 18, 2020, Boli Zhang ne banne baafulumya okunoonyereza okwategereza eddagala ly'obujjanjabi (WM) lyokka n'eryo erigattiddwako WM ne TCM.
Baakizuula nti ekiseera ekyetaagisa okuwonawo, obubonero bwonna obubaawo, n'okufuna mu ddwaliro kyamala ekiseera kitono nnyo mu abo abaali mu kibinja ky'abasawo abaalina obujjanjabi mu by'ekisawo okusinga abo abaali mu kibinja ky'abasawo abaalina obujjanjabi mu by'ekisawo.
Ekisinga okwegendereza, omuwendo gw'obubonero obwakendeera (okuva ku butono okutuuka ku bukambwe) gwali wansi nnyo mu kibiina kya WM+TCM okusinga mu kibiina kya WM yokka (7.4% vs 46.2%) era n'okufa kwaali wansi mu kibiina kya WM+TCM okusinga mu kibiina kya WM yokka (8.8% vs 39%).
Kyokka, obukuumi n'obutonde bw'eddagala eriyitibwa TCM bwetaaga okukolebwa ku kigero ekinene era mu bifo bingi.
Ekirala kye njagala kwe kulaba engeri gye gikola era n'okulaga ebintu ebikola obulungi mu bujjanjabi bwa TCM oba mu bujjanjabi obw'ekigendererwa, bwe kiba kisoboka.
Abalwadde abasinga obungi abazuuliddwa oba abakakasibwa okuba ne COVID-19 beeraliikirivu olw'obulwadde buno obw'obusaasaanya ennyo era obuviirako ekikangabwa, ate n'abo abali mu kaduukulu bawulira obutali bumativu, ekiwuubaalo, n'obusungu.
Okugatta ku ekyo, obubonero bw'obulwadde ng'omusujja, hypoxia, n'okukoowa awamu n'ebizibu ebirala ebiva mu bujjanjabi ng'obutaba na tulo ebiva mu kukozesa eddagala eriyitibwa corticosteroids, bisobola okuleetera omuntu okweraliikirira ennyo n'okweraliikirira.
Mu kaseera akasooka aka SARS, waliwo ebirwadde eby'obwongo, omuli okwennyamira, okweraliikirira, okutya, okusoomooza, obubonero bw'obwongo, okutabuka, n'okuttibwa.
Okuzuula abantu be yayanjula n'okwekweka, ng'ekitundu ky'obujjanjabi bw'abantu mu kulwanyisa ekirwadde kya COVID-19, kiyinza okuleetera abantu okweraliikirira n'okuwulira nti balina obunafu olw'engeri obulwadde obwo gye buyinza okusaasaana, okwekweka, n'okuvumirirwa kw'ab'eŋŋanda zaabwe ne mikwano gyabwe.
N'olwekyo, obujjanjabi bw'obulamu obw'obwongo bulina okuweebwa abalwadde ba COVID-19, abantu be bateebereza, n'abo be basanga, n'abantu abalala bonna abali mu bwetaavu.
Obuyambi mu by'omwoyo bulina okuzingiramu okutandikawo ttiimu y'obwongo eyalimu ab'emikono emingi, okuba n'empuliziganya ennungi n'okubuulirirwa entakera ku kizibu kya SARS-CoV-2, n'okuteekateeka enzijanjaba n'okukozesa ebyuma n'enkola z'ekikugu mu by'obulamu okwewala okusemberera abantu.
Eddagala erigasa lyetaagisa nnyo okusala ensingo y'okusaasaanya okuva mu nsiri y'ebisolo n'abantu abalina akawuka okutuuka ku bantu abalina akawuka era nga emirundi mingi liyamba mu kujjanjaba endwadde eziva ku bulwadde bwa siriimu.
Okukola n'omusaayi gw'ekika kya S, ogusobola okuwangula obulwadde buno mu kiseera ekitali kya wala era ogusobola okutaasa obulwadde buno okuva ku SARS-CoV.
Ku SARS, eddagala erigema obulamu lyateekebwako mu bisolo.
Kyokka, obuwanguzi bw'eddagala lino mu bantu abakulu n'omulembe ogw'okugezesebwa okw'obulabe era n'obukuumi bwalyo eri obulwadde bw'akawuka ka zoonotic bulina okusooka okussibwako essira nga tebannaba kutandika ku nkola ya bujjanjabi.
Kino kiyinzika okuba nga kiva ku kuba nti SARS yaggwaawo emyaka 17 emabega era nga tewali mulwadde mulala yenna ayogeddwako okuva olwo.
Wabula, obuwuka bwa MERS obwa bulijjo n'obw'ekigero bweyongera mu Middle East era ne busasaana mu bitundu ebirala olw'okuba obuwuka obwo bukyali mu bitundu gye busangibwa.
Amagezi g'okukuza abantu gakulembedde MERS nga bakozesa obuwuka obutakwatibwa, DNA plasmids, obuwuka obuleeta obuwuka, obuwuka obufaanana ng'obw'ekika ekimu, n'obutundu bw'obwomu bw'obutabuwuka era ng'ebimu ku byo byatambuziddwa mu bisolo.
Okukulaakulanya eddagala erirwanyisa SARS-CoV-2 eririna obukuumi era erikola mu bantu abatalina bulwadde buno, mulimu mu bwangu era kikulu nnyo mu kulabirira ekirwadde kino.
Kyokka, obuzibu buno tebuyinza kugonjoolwa kyangu olw'ebbanga eddene eryetaagisa okukola eddagala (emyezi 18 ku buli muntu) n'enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi eza CoV.
Ng'obulwadde obuppya, COVID-19 yatandika okweyoleka mu bujjuvu mu nkumi n'enkumi z'abalwadde.
Mu mbeera ezisinga obungi, omuntu aba afudde asobola okuwona mpolampola nga talina kizibu kyonna.
Kyokka, okufaananako SARS ne MERS, COVID-19 nayo erina akakwate n'obubenje n'okufa okw'amaanyi mu balwadde abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
N'olwekyo, okuteekawo enkola y'okuteebereza endwadde kikulu nnyo eri ebitongole ebikuuma obulamu okusobola okussa mu nkola enkola y'ebyobulamu, naddala mu bitundu ebiriko eby'obugagga ebitono.
Okusinziira ku bigezo by'ekisawo ebibadde birangirirwa okutuuka kati, ebintu bino wammanga biyinza okukosa oba okwetaba n'ebirwadde bya COVID-19 (Ekitundu 3):
Obukulu: Obukulu kye kintu ekisinga obukulu mu kulagirira ku SARS, nga bwe kiri ne ku COVID-19.
COVID-19 yasinga kujjira abo abaali wakati w'emyaka 30 ne 65 nga 47.7% baali basajja abaali basussa emyaka 50 mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku bantu 8,866 abaakosebwa ekirwadde kino nga bwe kiragiddwa waggulu.
Abalwadde abali mu ddwaaliro eryo batera okuba n'ebizibu eby'amaanyi era nga bakaddiye okusinga abo abataali mu ddwaaliro eryo (omutindo gw'emyaka 66 ku buli 51), ekiraga nti emyaka gye gisinga okuba ku mulembe mu mbeera y'abalwadde ba COVID-19.
Omusajja n'omukazi: SARS-CoV-2 ekwata abasajja okusinga abakazi (0.31/100,000 vs. 0.27/100,000), nga bwe kyogeddwako waggulu.
Okufaanagana n'ebizibu: Abalwadde ba COVID-19 abeetaaga okujjanjabibwa ennyo balina obusobozi obw'okufuna obuvune mu mutima n'obutayimba bulungi.
Obulwadde bw'omutima nabwo bwe businga okutta abantu abafuna SARS.
Kigambibwa nti SARS-CoV-2 era esobola okukwata ku colangiocytes eziriko ACE2-positive, ekiyinza okuviirako obukookolo bw'ekibumba mu balwadde ba COVID-19.
Kikulu okukijjukira nti emyaka n'obulwadde ebirina kye biyamba biyinza okuba nga bikwatagana era nga biyambagana.
Ebitafaanana n'ebiragiddwa mu laavu: Omutindo gwa protein eya C-reactive (CRP) mu musaayi gulaga obukambwe bw'obulwadde oba obuvune mu mubiri era gusobola okuba ekiviirako obulwadde, okujjanjaba, n'okuwona.
Enkolagana wakati w'omutindo gwa CRP n'obunnyogovu n'ennyonyoona ya COVID-19 nayo yateekebwako.
Okugatta ku ekyo, okulinnya kwa lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), ne creatine kinase (CK) nabyo bisobola okuyamba mu kulagula ebivudde mu kusalawo.
Enzyme zino zisaasaanyizibwa mu bitundu eby'enjawulo, naddala mu mutima ne mu kiwundu, era zifulumiziddwa mu kukyuka kw'ebitundu eby'omubiri.
N'olwekyo, enziimu zino ze zimu ku ezo ezimanyiddwa ennyo eziraga obutali butuukirivu bw'omutima n'obw'omusaayi.
Obubonero obusookerwako: Ekifaananyi kya thorax n'enkula y'obubonero bw'ekisenge ky'omubiri kirina okutwalibwa awamu n'ebirala okusobola okuteebereza ebiva mu COVID-19 n'ebizibu ebiyinza okuvaamu.
Okukozesa steroids: Nga bwe twalabye waggulu, steroids zikozesebwa nnyo ng'eddagala ery'okuyamba mu kulwanyisa endwadde eziriko obuwuka okusobola okukendeeza ku bukambwe bw'obulwadde obuleeta obulwadde.
Olw'okuba eddagala lya corticosteroids lyakozesebwa nnyo mu balwadde ba SARS, abantu bangi abawona obulwadde buno bawona obulwadde bw'amagumba n'okulemererwa obulamu bwabwe bwonna.
N'olwekyo, singa kiba kyetaagisa, steroids zirina kukozesebwa mu ddagala erya wansi era okumala akaseera katono mu balwadde ba COVID-19.
Okwennyamidde: Nga bwe kyayogeddwako waggulu, mu kiseera kya COVID-19, abalwadde bangi bafunye okweraliikirira olw'okuba bafunye obutategeeragana obw'amaanyi n'okumala ekiseera kiwanvu nga bali mu kkomera, era nga balabye n'okufa kw'ab'eŋŋanda zaabwe n'abalwadde abalala.
Okubuulirira okw'ekikugu n'obuyambi obw'ekiseera ekiwanvu birina okuweebwa okuyamba omulwadde oyo okuwona okuva mu kweraliikirira n'okuddayo mu bulamu obwa bulijjo.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza ku bantu okukoleddwa, COVID-19 erina ekifaananyi kya siriimu ekyawukana ku kya SARS.
Ng'oggyeko okwekulaakulanya mu kkubo ly'omukka ery'omunsi, SARS-CoV-2 esobola okwekulaakulanya mu kkubo ly'omukka ery'oku waggulu era n'okuleeta obubonero obutonotono oba obutaliiko mu ntandikwa y'obulwadde, nga bwe kiri eri CoV endala ezivaako ekikulukuto.
N'olwekyo, mu mitendera egy'okusooka oba mu kiseera eky'okukwekamu, omuntu alina obulwadde bw'akawuka asobola okuzaala obulwadde mu bungi mu bulamu bwe obwa bulijjo, ekiviirako obuzibu obw'amaanyi mu kuziyiza ekirwadde.
Kyokka, okusasaanya SARS-CoV kukkirizibwa okubaawo ng'omulwadde alwadde nnyo era abasinga tebajja kubeerawo mu mitendera egyasooka.
N'olwekyo, ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kya maanyi nnyo era kyangu okufuga okusinga ekirwadde kya SARS.
Mu kiseera kino, okufuba okunene ku mulembe mu China, omuli okusazaamu ekibuga Wuhan n'ebibuga ebiriraanyeewo awamu n'okusiba kumpi abantu bonna mu ssuubi ery'okusazaamu SARS-CoV-2.
Wadde nga kino kivuddeko ebikolwa eby'amaanyi eby'okunafuya ebyenfuna n'ebirala mu ggwanga, omuwendo gw'abalwadde abappya gukendedde, ekiraga nti ekirwadde kino kikendedde.
Okusuubira okungi kulaga nti ekirwadde kino kijja kukoma mu Maaki era nti kijja kukendeera mu myezi esatu oba esatu.
Kyokka, abakugu abalala tebakitwala bwe batyo.
Paul Hunter ne banne bateebereza nti COVID-19, ekirabika ng'ekyayinza okusasaana okusinga SARS, tekigenda kukoma mu 2020.
Ira Longini, et al. baakola enkola ey'okulowooza ku kivaamu mu kawuka era ne bagamba nti SARS-CoV-2 esobola okukosa ebitundu bibiri ku bisatu eby'abantu mu nsi yonna.
Ekibinja ky'abanoonyereza mu Canada kyalaga nti SARS-CoV-2 yakeberebwa mu bwasutiini ne mu nnyingo z'abalwadde abaawona ne bava mu ddwaliro wiiki bbiri emabega, ekiraga nti akawuka kano kasobola okudda mu mbeera y'omusujja, nga kakwatagana n'akawuka ka siriimu.
Wadde kiri kityo, obubonero obuwa essuubi mu China, bwe bujjako nga bw'olaba ku muwendo gw'abantu abafuna obulwadde obufaanana ng'obwo, bulaga nti enkola y'omu kiseera kino eyinza okuba ng'etambula bulungi.
Ebola yali erina okuviirako abantu akakadde kalamba okufa, era nga kimu kya kubiri ku abo abafa.
Kyokka, olw'okuba abantu baateekebwa mu bifo eby'ekyama era ne baggibwawo mu bitundu eby'enjawulo, mu nkomerero obulwadde obwo bwali buyinza okuwonyezebwawo.
Kiyinzika okuba nti, okufaananako SARS-CoV, SARS-CoV-2 yafuuka ekirwadde ekikendeeza ku busobozi bw'okukwata abantu era n'ekyavaamu n'ekoma okuzikirira oba n'afuuka ekirwadde ekitatera kubeera mu bantu.
Okugeraageranya obulwadde bwa COVID-19 n'obwo bwa SARS ne MERS kulabikiddwa wammanga (Fig. 5).
SARS-CoV-2 ekwatulwa mangu okuyita mu kukasuka oba okusimula, era nga kisoboka okuyita mu kusemberera obutereevu ebintu ebiba nga byonoonese.
Akawuka kano era kaalabikira mu nsiri, era kino kireetawo engeri empya ey'okusaasaamu akawuka ako, nga kino kye kiwona obusawo.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa gye buvuddeko ku bantu 138 kulaga nti 41% ku bo bayinza okuba nga baali balwadde, nga muno mwe mwali abalwadde 17 abaali balwadde edda n'abo abaalina endwadde endala awamu n'abo abajjanjaba 40.
N'olwekyo, enkola ey'okwerinda erina okukolebwa okusobola okukuuma abantu, naddala abo abawa obujjanjabi, abakozi b'eby'obuntu, ab'eŋŋanda, bakozi bannaabwe, n'abo abafuna enkolagana n'omulwadde oba omuntu alina obulwadde.
Engeri esooka ey'okwerinda okuwanvuwaza akawuka kwe kukozesa masiki, ka kube masiki z'abasawo oba masiki z'abasibe N95 (ennamba y'omugendo eya 1860s) okuziyiza okusaasaana kw'akawuka.
Ebikolobero bino bikakasa nti amazzi agava mu muntu asobola okukwatibwa obulwadde tegagenda mu bbanga oba ku bintu ebirina omukka, ne gasobola okusasaana mu bantu abalala.
Kyokka, masiki ya N95 (ennamba ya 1860s) y'esobola okukuuma eri ekyokumansira kya virion ezirimu obuwanvu obuto okuva ku 10 n'okutuuka ku 80 nm, nga kati obuwanvu bwa 5% bwokka; SARS-CoV-2 eringa SARS-CoV mu bunene, nga zombi zirina obuwanvu bwa 85 nm.
Olw'okuba obuwuka busobola okuyingira mu masiki z'okulongoosa nga zikoleddwa mu kifuba, abasawo abalina abalwadde be balina okwambala N95 (ennamba ya 1860s) mu kifo ky'amasiki.
Ng'oggyeko ebibikka ku maaso, abajjanjabi balina okwambala ebibukka ebisaanira okwongera okukendeeza okukwatagana n'akawuka.
Ensawo era esobola okukwata omuntu okuyita mu maaso.
Nga 22 Jjanwali 2020, omusawo yakwatibwa ekirwadde kya SARS-CoV-2 wadde nga yali ayambadde akaweweera ka N95; akawuka kano kaali kasobola okuyingira mu mubiri gwe okuyita mu kuvimba kw'amaaso.
N'olwekyo, abasawo basaanidde okwambala eby'okwekwata mu maaso ebiyamba omuntu okulaba obulungi oba eby'okukuuma amaaso nga bakolagana n'abalwadde.
Eri abantu bonna mu bitundu ebirwadde oba ebiyinza okuba nga birwadde, kikubiriza nnyo buli muntu okunaaba engalo ze n'obucaafu emirundi mingi okusinga bwe kimanyiddwa, okufuba okusigala awaka ng'ali mu buwambe, n'okwewala okusisinkana abantu abalina obulwadde.
Okubeera empi ku lugenda lwa ffuuti ssatu kukkirizibwa okubeera okw'omugaso eri omulwadde.
Ebikolwa bino biyinza okuba eby'omugaso mu kukendeeza akabi ak'okusaasaana kw'akawuka era n'okusigala nga tukyali balamu.
Wadde nga SARS-CoV-2 kiwuka kippya mu bantu, okufaanagana kwayo n'okwa SARS-CoV, nga bwe kyalagibwa nga 7 Janwali 2020, kirina okuba nga kijjukizo eri China, ekyajjukira ennyo SARS mu 2003.
Kyokka, nga 19 Jjanwali 2020, akulira ekitebe ky'okuziyiza endwadde mu Wuhan yakkakkanya abantu nti akawuka kano kalimu obunafu bw'okusasaana n'obutono bw'okusaasaanya okuva ku muntu okudda ku muntu era nti okutangira n'okumalawo obulwadde si kizibu.
Obubaka buno buweweeza nnyo abantu, naddala ng'eggwanga lyonna litegeka Embaga y'Obubaale, era nga kino kiseera kya kabi nnyo okuziyiza ekirwadde kino mu Wuhan.
Ekitongole ekirwanyisa endwadde mu China kyetaaga okuyigira ku kino n'okukola enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi mu biseera eby'omu maaso.
