Okwongera ku bisaanyizo by'okunoonyereza ku kuteeberezebwa n'ku kakasa kwa COVID-19 kwetaagisa
Nga 6 Febwali 2020, ttiimu yaffe yafulumya ekitabo ekikuwa amagezi amangu ku ngeri y'okwekebejja n'okwekebejja ekirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe 2019 (2019-nCoV). Ekitabo kino kyesigamye ku bumanyirivu bwaffe era ky'ekikozesebwa okulwanyisa ekirwadde kino mu nsi yonna.
Wadde nga coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) bulwadde obusuubirwa, okumanya kwaffe n'obumanyirivu bw'obulwadde buno bweyongedde okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okukolebwa n'okumanya kwe tulina mu nkola y'ekisawo; n'olwekyo, enkola z'okuzuula n'okujjanjaba nazo zikyusiddwa buli kiseera.
Mu bbaluwa eno, tuddamu ekimu ku byayogeddwa mu buwandiike bwaffe era tuwa amagezi ku ngeri y'okunoonyerezaamu "abaalwadde abateeberezebwa" ne "abo abakakasibwa" okusinziira ku buwandiike bwa COVID-19 (verisi ey'omusanvu) eyakubibwa ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu ekya People's Republic of China.
Mu December wa 2019, ekirwadde kya coronavirus ekyamanyika 2019 (2019-nCoV) kyaleetawo kawumpuli, kati mu lujjudde eyitibwa coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) era ekirwadde kino kiyitibwa coronavirus severe acute respiratory syndrome 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Nga 11 omwezi gwa March, 2020, WHO yannyonnyola nti COVID-19 yali mulwadde.
Okulwanyisa obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2, ttiimu yaffe yatandikawo amagezi amangu ago era ne gafulumizibwa ku mutimbagano mu Military Medical Research nga Febwali 6, 2020.
Akatabo ako kaaliko ebintu bingi ebiwuniikiriza okuva lwe kaafulumizibwa.
Wabula, kikulu okukijjukira nti COVID-19 ndwadde empya, okumanya kwaffe n'okumanya kweyongedde okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okukolebwa n'obumanyirivu mu nkola y'ekisawo; n'olwekyo, enkola z'okwekebejja n'okujjanjaba nazo zikyusibwa.
