Omutwalo gw'abantu okusisinkana ogwakubirizibwa ebitongole bya gavumenti ya Amerika n'ebitongole by'ebyobulamu gwakendeezebwako mangu okuva ku bantu 250 (nga tewali COVID-19 eyaliwo mu kitundu) okutuuka ku bantu 50, ate n'oluvannyuma okutuuka ku bantu 10.
