Oluvannyuma, ekibinja ky'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abatali ba mu nsi eyo kyazuulibwa, nga kutandikira ku bantu 16 abaali bakakasiddwa nti balina obulwadde mu Lombardy nga 21 Febwaliri. Nga 22 Febwali, Minisitule ya Minisita yalangirira etteeka eppya erigenda okukomya obulwadde, omuli okutereka abantu abasukka mu 50,000 okuva mu bibuga 11 mu bukiikakkono bwa Italy.
Ssaabaminisita Giuseppe Conte yagamba nti: "Mu bitundu ebirimu obulwadde, abantu tebakkirizibwa kuyingira na kuvaayo.
Okuyimiriza emirimu n'emizannyo mu kitundu kino". Nga 4 Ogw'okusatu, gavumenti ya Italy yalagira amasomero n'amatendekero g'obuyigirize okuggalawo mu ggwanga lyonna ng'Abataliya batuuka ku bantu 100.
Emizannyo gyonna emikulu, omuli n'omuzannyo gw'omupiira ogwa Serie A, gyandibagaddemu okutuusa mu mwezi gwa Apuli, naye nga 9 Ogw'okusatu, emizannyo gyonna gijja kuyimirizibwa okumala omwezi mulamba.
Ku nga 11 March, Ssaabaminisita Conte yalagira okuyimiriza emirimu gy'ebyobusuubuzi gyonna okuggyako amaduuka amanene n'amaduuka. Ku nga 6 March, Ekitongole ky'Abawala eky'Abawala mu Italy ekiyitibwa Ssiccolo di Anestesia, Analgesia, Resuscitazione e Terapia Intensiva (SIAARTI) kyafulumya amagezi agaweebwa abasawo ku ngeri y'okukozesaamu enkola ya triase.
Ku 19 Maaki, Italy yawangula China ng'ensi erina abantu abasinga okufa olwa coronavirus oluvannyuma lw'okusaasaanya abantu 3,405 abafudde mu bulwadde buno.
Nga Maaki 22, Russia yatumibwa okutwala ennyonyi z'amagye omwenda ezaalimu eby'obujjanjabi e Italy.
Nga 5 omwezi gwa April, waabaddewo abantu 128,948 abakakasiddwa nti balina obulwadde buno, abantu 15,887 bafudde, n'abantu 21,815 abawonye mu Italy, nga abasinga obungi ku bano babeera mu kitundu kya Lombardy.
Alipoota ya CNN egamba nti ekireese omuwendo gw'abantu abafa, ye ndowooza y'abantu abakaddiye mu Italy n'obutaba na ngeri y'okukebera buli muntu yenna alina akawuka ka siriimu.
Okusooka, engeri y'Obwongereza ey'okuddamu okulwanyisa ekirwadde kino y'emu ku y'ensi ezisinga okuba nga tezeetedde, era okutuusa nga Maaki 18, 2020, gavumenti ya Bungereza teyaliiko kizibu kyonna ku bantu baayo.
N'ekivuddemu, gavumenti yavumirirwa olw'obutaba na bbugumu nga baddamu ku nsonga z'abantu. Nga Maaki 16, Ssaabaminisita Boris Johnson yalangirira okuyimiriza okutambula kwonna n'okwekwataganya n'abantu era n'alagira abantu okukola emirimu gyabwe awaka, bwe kiba kisoboka, n'okwewala ebifo gamba nga pubs, amaduuka n'ebizimbe by'okuzannyamu emizannyo.
Nga 20 omwezi gwa March, gavumenti yalangirira nti ebifo byonna eby'okwesanyusaamu, gamba nga pubs n'ebifo eby'okukozesa obulungi omubiri, byali birina okuggalwa amangu ddala nga bwe kisoboka, era n'eyama okusasula ebitundu 80% ku misolo gy'abakozi okutuusa ku £2,500 buli mwezi okusobola okwewala ebbula ly'emirimu mu kaseera kano. Nga 23 omwezi gwa March, Ssaabaminisita yalangirira enkola y'okusiiga abantu mu mbeera embi ey'obuntu, ng'agaana abantu okusisinkana abantu abasukka mu babiri era n'okukendeeza ku ntambula n'ebweru ku bintu ebikulu byokka.
Okwawukana ku nkola ezaasooka, amateeka gano gafuulibwa amakakali nga poliisi ebawa enkizi n'okubasalawo.
Bizineesi ezisinga zaalagirwa okuggalwa, okuggyako ezo ezaatwalibwanga okuba "ennene", omuli amaduuka amanene, amaduuka ag'eddagala, amabanka, amaduuka ag'ebintu eby'omu ngalo, sitenseni, n'emirimu gy'okuzimba.
Nga 20 omwezi gwa Jjanwali, akawuka ka COVID-19 kaakasanguzibwa mu ssaza ly'omu masekkati g'e Washington, mu musajja eyava e Wuhan nga 15 omwezi guno.
Nga 29 omwezi guno, White House Coronavirus Task Force yassibwawo.
Nga 31 omwezi ogwedde, gavumenti ya Trump yalangirira embeera ey'obudde ey'obulamu bw'abantu era n'eteekawo obukwakkulizo ku bantu abava mu China.
Nga 28 Jjanwali 2020, ekitongole ekirwanyisa endwadde, ekitongole ekiramuzi ekikwasisa eby'obulamu mu gavumenti ya Amerika, kyagamba nti kyafuna ekikemo kyabyo.
Wadde kiri kityo, Amerika yalwawo nnyo okutandika okugezesa ekirwadde kino, ne kiba nti tekyategeerekeka bulungi nti ekirwadde ekyo kyali kibaluseewo.
Okugezesa kwava ku bukulu bw'ebikozesebwa ebigezesebwa ebifulumizibwa gavumenti mu Febwali, obutaba na gavumenti ekkiriza ebikozesebwa ebigezesebwa ebitava mu gavumenti (mu bayizi, amakampuni, n'amalwaliro) mu Febwali, n'ebiteeso ebikugira abantu okutuukiriza ebisaanyizo by'okugezesa mu ntandikwa ya Maaki (nga oluvannyuma lw'ekyo waliwo ebiragiro by'abasawo).
Nga 27 Ogwobwe, The Washington Post yategeeza nti waaliwo ebigezo ebitawera 4,000 mu Amerika.
Nga March 13, The Atlantic yagamba nti ebigezo ebitawera 14,000 byali byakolebwa.
Nga March 22, Associated Press kyawandiika: "Abantu bangi abalina obubonero era nga ne badokita beeyisa bulungi balinze okumala essaawa oba ennaku eziwerako okugezesebwa". Oluvannyuma lw'okufa kw'omuntu asooka mu Amerika okwategeezebwa mu Washington nga Febwali 29, gavana Jay Inslee yalangirira embeera ey'obutabanguko, ekyagobererwa amangu mu mawanga amalala.
Amasomero mu kitundu kya Seattle gaaggyamu amasomo nga March 3, era mu makkati ga March, amasomero mu ggwanga lyonna gaaggalwawo. Nga March 6, 2020, Amerika yategeezebwa ku nkulaakulana ya coronavirus empya mu ggwanga lino ekibinja ky'abakugu mu by'obulwadde mu Imperial College London.
Ku lunaku lwe lumu, Pulezidenti Trump yalagira etteeka eriyitibwa Coronavirus Preparedness and Response Supplemental Appropriations Act, eryawadde obuwumbi $8.3 mu nsimbi z'obuyambi eri ebitongole by'obwannakyewa okwanukula ekirwadde kino.
Kkampuni z'ebadduuka z'ebadduuka z'abakozi, z'eggyako enkuŋŋaana, era ne zikubiriza abakozi okukola okuva waka.
Emikolo n'embeera z'emizannyo byagolebwa. Nga 11 Maaki, Trump yalangirira ekkomo ku ntambula ku bitundu bya Bulaaya ebisinga, okuggyako Bungereza, okumala ennaku 30, nga ku 13 Maaki, lyali liddiridde.
Olunaku olwaddirira, yaggyawo okuwera okwo n'ateekawo ensi za Bungereza ne Ireland.
Nga Maaki 13, yalangirira embeera ey'obwetaavu mu ggwanga nga gavumenti esobola okufuna ssente ez'okuddamu mu bizibu.
Okuva nga 15 Maaki, amaduuka mangi gaggiddwawo oba ne gakendebwako essaawa z'emirimu mu Amerika yonna mu kugezaako okukendeeza ku kusaasaana kw'akawuka.
Nga 17 Maaki, ekirwadde kino kyali kikakasiddwa mu mawanga gonna 50 ne mu Disitulikiti y'e Columbia. nga 23 Maaki, New York City yali erina abantu 10,700 abaalina ekirwadde kino, nga kino kisinga omuwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa mu South Korea.
Nga 25 Ogw'okusatu, gavana wa New York yagamba nti okukendeeza ku bbeereere kyalinga kiyambye kubanga omuwendo gw'abaalwadde gwe baali basuubira okubalukawo gwalinnya emirundi ebiri okuva ku 2.0 ku 4.7.
Nga 28 Maaki, waliwo abantu 32,308 abaakakasibwa nti balina akawuka ka coronavirus mu New York City era abantu 672 be baafa. Nga 26 Maaki, Amerika yategeezebwa okuba n'abantu abaakakasibwa nti balina akawuka ka coronavirus okusinga ensi endala yonna, nga mw'otwalidde China ne Italy.
Okusinziira ku lipoota z'amawulire ku 30 omwezi ogwa March, Pulezidenti wa Amerika Trump yasalawo okwongera okuteekawo amateeka ku by'okusiba abantu mu maka okutuusa nga 30 omwezi gwa April.
Ku lunaku olwo lwennyini, eryato eriyitibwa USNS Comfort, eririmu amalwaliro agasukka mu 1,000, lyatuuka mu kibuga New York.
Ku 3 Apuli, Amerika yalimu abantu 884 abaafiriddwa ekirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe mu ssaawa 24.
Mu New York State, omuwendo gw'abantu abaakakwatibwa gwasukka 100,000 nga 3 Apuli. White House yanenyezebwa olw'okutyoboola ebiteeso n'okufuga obubaka ng'eragira abakungu b'ebyobulamu n'abasayansi okulambika ebyogerwa mu lujjudde n'ebitabo ebikwata ku kawuka mu ofiisi ya Vice President Mike Pence.
Mu bujjuvu, okusiima Trump mu ngeri gy'akuumamu obuzibu, kwawukanamu wakati w'ab'oludda oluvuganya.
Abakungu ba Amerika n'abamu ku bantu abalala bavumirira eky'okuggyamu eby'amaguzi bya Amerika ebikulu okuva mu China, omuli n'eby'obusawo.
Okunoonyereza ku ngeri y'okutambula kw'ennyonyi kukozeseddwa okukuba kaadi n'okulowooza ku ngeri y'okusaasaamu era kwafulumizibwa mu The Journal of Travel Medicine mu makkati ga Jjanwali 2020.
Okusinziira ku biwandiiko bya 2018 okuva mu International Air Transport Association, abantu abava e Wuhan abasinga obungi babeera mu Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo ne Taipei.
Dubai, Sydney, ne Melbourne nabyo byogerwako ng'ebifo ebimanyiddwa ennyo abantu abava e Wuhan.
Bali y'esinga obunafu mu mbeera y'obutebenkevu mu bibuga 20 ebikyasinze okubeerako, ng'ate ebibuga mu Australia bye bisinga okuba ebyenkevu.
Kigambibwa nti waliwo bingi ebizuuliddwa ku COVID-19, era nti Australia ejja kwongera amaanyi ku kukuuma ensalo n'empuliziganya mu kwanukula obulwadde buno.
Nga Maaki 21, Australia yalangirira nti abantu baali mu mbeera ey'obutaba na bulamu.
Olw'okuba ebisale by'entambula mu bantu byateekebwawo mu Wuhan ne Hubei, amawanga agamu gagenda okuggya abantu baago n'abakozi baayo okuva mu bitundu ebyo, okusingira ddala okuyita mu ntambula y'ebidduka okuva mu nsi gye baavudde, nga bakkirizibwa ab'obuyinza mu China.
Canada, Amerika, Japan, India, Sri Lanka, Australia, France, Argentina, Germany, ne Thailand ze zimu ku nsi ezisoose okukola enteekateeka ez'okufulumya abantu baayo.
Pakistan egamba nti tejja kuwaayo bantu baayo okuva mu China.
Nga February 7, Brazil yaggya aba Brazil 34 oba ab'omu maka g'aba Brazil, ng'oggyeko aba Poland bana, Omuchina, n'Omumbejja.
Ab'omu Poland, China, ne Buyindi baasiibulwa mu Poland, gye baasibira nga bagenda e Brazil.
Aba Brazil abaagenda e Wuhan baakuumirwa mu kkomera ly'amagye eriri okumpi ne Brasília.
Ku lunaku lwe lumu, abantu 215 okuva mu Canada (176 ku nnyonyi esooka ne 39 ku nnyonyi eyokubiri eyapangisibwa gavumenti ya Amerika) baakuumibwa okuva e Wuhan ne batwalibwa ku CFB Trenton okwekweka okumala wiiki bbiri.
Nga February 11, ennyonyi endala erina abantu 185 okuva e Wuhan yakwata abantu okuva e Canada ku CFB Trenton.
Ab'obuyinza ba Australia baaddusa abantu baabwe 277 nga 3 ne 4 omwezi oguyita mu Kisibo kya Christmas Island Detention Centre, ekyakyusibwa ne kifuulibwa ekituumibwa okwekuumisa, gye baamala ennaku 14.
Ennyonyi y'e New Zealand eyadduka okuva mu bbanga yatuuka mu Auckland nga Febwali 5; abaali mu nnyonyi (nga mw'otwalidde n'abamu okuva mu Australia ne Pacific) baali bakwatiddwa mu kifo ekikessi ku mwalo gw'amagye e Whangaparoa, mu bukiikakkono bwa Auckland.
Nga 15 February, Amerika yalangirira nti egenda kuggya abantu baayo bonna ku mmeeri ya Diamond Princess.
Nga Febwali 21, ennyonyi eyali etisse abantu b'omu Canada 129 abaali bavudde ku Diamond Princess yakwata mu Trenton, Ontario.
Ku ntandikwa ya March, gavumenti ya India yatandika okuggya abantu baayo mu Iran. Ku March 14, ennyonyi eya South African Airways eyapangisibwa gavumenti ya South Africa yazzaayo abantu baayo 112.
Okukebera kwa ddagala kwaliwo nga tebannavaayo era abantu bana aba South Africa abaalabika nga balina akabonero ka coronavirus baasibibwa mu bbanga okukendeeza ku bulabe.
Ab'omu South Africa bokka abazzeemu nga tebalina buzibu be baddayo.
Okusinziira ku biva mu kukeberebwa, abantu bonna mu South Africa, omuli ab'omu mmotoka, abagoba b'ennyonyi, abakozi b'omu wooteeri, poliisi n'abaserikale abaakola omulimu gw'obuyambi, baakuumibwa era ne balabirirwa okumala ennaku 14 mu kifo ekiyitibwa The Ranch Resort.
Ku 20 Maaki, Amerika yatandika okuggya amagye mu Iraq olw'ekirwadde.
Nga Febwali 5, Minisitule y'ensonga z'ebweru ey'e China yagamba nti amawanga 21 (nga mw'otwalidde Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad ne Tobago, Misiri, ne Iran) gaali gaweereza obuyambi eri China.
Abayizi b'omu China mu yunivasite ez'enjawulo mu Amerika beegasse okutwala obuyambi mu bitundu bya China ebiriko akawuka, wamu n'ekibiina ekyeegasse okuva mu kibuga Chicago; baategeeza nti baasobola okusindika amasimu ga N95 50,000 mu malwaliro mu ssaza ly'e Hubei nga 30 Ogw'Okutandika. Ekibiina ky'obuyambi obwa namuntu, Direct Relief, nga kikwatagana ne FedEx, kyasindika amasimu g'omu maaso 200,000 n'ebirala ebikozesebwa okwekuuma, omuli n'engalo n'ebikozesebwa, okuyita mu ntambula y'ennyonyi ey'amangu mu ddwaliro lya Union Hospital mu Wuhan nga 30 Ogw'Okutandika.
Nga February 5, Bill ne Melinda Gates baalangirira okugaba obukadde 100 eri WHO okuwagira okunoonyereza ku njaga n'okulabirira abantu, n'okukuuma "abantu abali mu buzibu mu Afirika ne mu South Asia".
Interaksyon ekiriko nti gavumenti ya China yawaayo amasiki 200,000 eri Philippines nga 6 February, oluvannyuma lwa Seneta Richard Gordon okusindika amasiki obukadde 3.16 e Wuhan.
Nga February 19, ekibiina kya Singapore Red Cross kyalangirira nti kyali kigenda kusindika obuyambi bwa doola obukadde 2.26 mu China.
Japan yawaddeyo ebisawo by'amaaso omuli obukadde 1 mu Wuhan, Turkey yasindika ebikozesebwa eby'eddwaliro, Russia yasindika etoni z'ebikozesebwa eby'eddwaliro 13 mu Wuhan, Malaysia yawaddeyo obuyambi bw'engalo z'eddwaliro obukadde 18, Bugirimaani yasindika ebikozesebwa eby'eddwaliro omuli engoye 10,000, Amerika yawaddeyo etoni 17.8 ez'ebikozesebwa eby'eddwaliro mu China era n'eyongezaayo obukadde bwa doola 100 mu buyambi bw'ebyenfuna eri amawanga agalina obulwadde.
Mu Maaki, China, Cuba, ne Russia baasindika abasawo n'abakugu okuyamba Italy mu kulwanyisa ssenyiga omukambwe.
Omusuubuzi Jack Ma yatuma ebintu eby'okugezesa 1.1million, eby'okwekubisa mu maaso 6million, n'eby'okwambala 60,000 mu Addis Ababa, Ethiopia, okugabira African Union.
Oluvannyuma, yasindika ebikozesebwa ebigezesa 5,000, eby'okukuuma amaaso 100,000, n'ebikozesebwa okufuuyisa empewo 5 e Panama.
Ma era yawaayo obuyambi bw'eddagala eri Canada, Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia ne Czech Republic nga balaga obweraliikirivu ku mutindo gw'amasiki n'ebipimo ebikozesebwa mu kunoonyereza ebyakolebwa mu China.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, Spain yaggya mu nkola ebikemo 58,000 ebyakolebwa mu China eby'okugezesa ssenyiga omukambwe ebirina obutuufu bwa 30 ku buli kikumi; ate Netherlands yaggya mu nkola ebikemo 600,000 ebyakolebwa mu China ebirina obulemu.
Ate era, Belgium yaggyaayo masiki 100,000 ezaali ziteeberezebwa okuba nga zaava mu China, naye nga mu butuufu zaava mu Colombia.
Ku luuyi olulala, obuyambi bwa China bwasiimibwa mu bitundu bya Latin America ne Afirika. Nga 2 April, Banka y'ensi yonna yatongoza ebikwekweto by'obuyambi obw'amangu eri amawanga ageesimbye amagoba.
WHO yasiima nnyo okufuba kwa gavumenti ya China okufuga n'okumalawo ekirwadde kino.
WHO yatunuulira enjawulo wakati w'ekirwadde kya SARS mu 2002-2004 nga China eyattibwa olw'okuzibira ekirwadde kino n'obufuzi obuwabula obuva ku gavumenti ya China "okuweebwanga obuwiivu obuwerako okusobola okwewala okutya ng'olunaku lw'Eky'emyezi Oluggya lugenda kusembera".
Nga 23 January, ng'ayanukula ku kusalawo kwa gavumenti ya wakati okuwera entambula mu Wuhan, omubaka wa WHO Gauden Galea yagamba nti wadde nga kino "tekyali kya magezi eri WHO", naye "kyalina amakulu nnyo eri obumalirivu bw'okukomawo obulwadde mu bitundu ebirimu obulwadde obusinga obungi" era n'agamba nti "tekibangawo mu byafaayo by'ebyobulamu bw'abantu". Nga 30 January, oluvannyuma lw'okukakasibwa nti obulwadde buno bw'asaasaanira abantu ebweru wa China era n'omuwendo gw'abalwadde mu nsi endala bweyongerayongera, WHO yalangirira obulwadde buno nga PHEIC, ekikolwa eky'omukaaga okuva bwe kyabaawo mu 2009 ng'ekyaama ky'omusujja gw'embizzi kibaluse.
WHO akulira ekitongole kino Tedros Adhanom agamba nti PHEIC eyogerwako "kubanga wabaawo akabi akayinza okusaasaana mu nsi yonna, naddala mu mawanga agalina ssente entono n'agatali ku mulamwa, nga tegaliimu nkola ya bujjanjabi.
Mu kwanukula ku kukomya okutambula, Tedros yagamba nti "tewali nsonga yonna eyandireetedde okuteekawo emitendera egikosa okutambula n'obusuubuzi bw'ensi yonna" era nti "WHO tewabulawo lukusa lwa kukomya kutambula n'obutambula".
Nga February 5, WHO yasabye abantu mu nsi yonna okugaba obuwumbi bwa ddoola 675 ez'okuyingiza ssente mu nteekateeka z'okwetegeka mu mawanga ag'enfuna entono, nga bagamba nti kyetaagisa nnyo okuwagira amawanga "agalina enkola eyinza okuzuula abantu abalina akawuka ka siriimu singa kawumpuli ebalukawo".
Okugatta ku ekyo, Tedros yagamba nti "obunafu bwaffe businziira ku kifo ekisinga obunafu" era n'akubiriza amawanga gonna "okussaayo ssente leero oba okusasula ssente ezisingawo oluvannyuma". Mu lukung'aana lw'abamawulire olwa Febwali 11, WHO yalonda COVID-19 ng'erinnya ly'obulwadde.
Ku lunaku olwo lwennyini, Tedros yagamba nti Ssaabawandiisi w'ekibiina ky'amawanga amagatte, António Guterres, yakkirizza okuwaayo "okuddamu okw'amaanyi mu ngeri y'okukozesa amaanyi gonna agali mu kibiina ky'amawanga amagatte".
Oluvannyuma, UN yakyusawo Crisis Management Teams okusobozesa okwegatta kw'obuyambi bw'ekibiina ky'amawanga amagatte, nga WHO bw'egamba nti kijja kubayamba "okwemalira ku kujjanjaba abantu, ng'ate ebitongole ebirala bisobola okukozesa obumanyirivu bwabwe okugonjoola embeera z'abantu, eby'enfuna, n'embeera z'abantu".
Ku Lwokuna 14, ttiimu y'abanoonyereza ku bulwadde bw'ekirwadde ekikosa obulamu mu China nga bakulembeddwamu WHO yatongozebwa; ttiimu eno yalaga nti yajja okuteekawo abakugu mu nsi yonna ne WHO mu China basobole okuyambako mu kutereka endwadde mu ggwanga era n'okwetegereza "obuzito n'obubalwadde" nga bayita mu seminaali n'enkuŋŋaana z'ebitongole ebikwatagana n'ebyobulamu mu ggwanga n'okukyalira ebifo okusobola okumanya "obuyambi obuli mu bitundu ne mu disitulikiti, ebibuga ne mu byalo". Ku Lwokuna 25, WHO yalaga nti "ensi erina okukola ekisingawo okwetegekera ekirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe" era n'egamba nti, wadde nga kyali tekinnaba nga kyakuweebwa linnya lya kirwadde kino, amawanga galina "okubeera mu mbeera ey'okwetegekera".
Mu kweggyamu obulwadde obugenda mu maaso mu Iran, WHO yasindika Ekibinja ky'abanoonyereza ku bulwadde mu Iran okwekenneenya embeera. Nga Febwali 28, abakungu ba WHO baategeezezza nti ekibuuzo ku bulwadde bwa coronavirus mu nsi yonna kigenda kulondebwa okuva ku "kiwanvu" okudda ku "kiwanvu nnyo", nga kino kye kibuuzo ekisingayo okuba eky'obulabe era ekisinga okuba eky'akabi.
Mu kwogera, Mike Ryan, akulira enteekateeka z'omulwadde mu kiseera ekyo yalaga nti, "Kiseera kituuse buli gavumenti ku nsi okwolekagana n'ensonga eno: Beera bulindaala.
Akawuka kano kayinza okujja mu kifo kyo era olina okuba omwetegefu", era n'akubiriza nti okulwanyisa ekituufu kiyinza okuyamba ensi okwewala "ebizibu ebisinga okuba eby'amaanyi".
Ryan era agamba nti ebikwatagana ebiriko kati tebisobozesa bakungu ba bujjanjabi okulangirira nti obulwadde buno bwa mu nsi yonna, era n'agamba nti okulangirira ng'okwo kitegeeza nti "mu butereevu tukkiriza nti buli muntu ku nsi ajja kuba n'akawuka ka siriimu".
Nga 11 Maaki, WHO yalangirira nti ekirwadde kya coronavirus kyali kya bulwadde bwa nsi yonna.
Omukulu wa WHO yagamba nti WHO "yeeraliikirivu nnyo olw'omuwendo gw'abantu abafaako n'obukulu bw'obulwadde buno, n'obutakola bulungi". WHO yavumirirwa nnyo olw'obutabaako ky'ekozeewo ku bulwadde buno, omwali n'okulwawo okulangirira nti bwali bwa maanyi nnyo era ne kyetaagisa okuteekawo ekirwadde kino mu ngeri ey'ekikyayibwamu.
Omu ku baalabamu amaanyi mwe muli ekiwandiiko ekiriko emikono 733,000 nga 6 Ogwokuna, ekyaweerezebwa ku akulira w'ekitongole ky'obulamu ekya WHO Tedros Adhanom ng'amusaba ave ku buyinza.
Nga March 26, 2020, abakugu mu ddembe ly'obuntu mu mawanga amagatte baagamba nti balina okussa ekitiibwa mu ddembe ly'omuntu yenna mu kiseera ky'ekirwadde kya COVID-19.
Akakiiko kano kaagamba nti buli muntu alina eddembe okutaasa obulamu bwe era nti gavumenti erina obuvunaanyizibwa mu nsonga eno.
Ekibinja kino kigamba nti ebbula ly'obuyambi oba obujjanjabi tebirina kukozesebwa ng'ensonga ey'okusosola abantu.
Abakugu bagamba nti buli muntu alina eddembe okuba n'obulamu obulungi, omuli abantu abaliko obulemu, abantu ab'ebitongole ebitali bimu, bannamukadde, abayala, abayala amayumba, abo abali mu bwetaavu obw'amaanyi, abasibe, abanoonyi b'obubudamu, n'abantu abalala abeetaaga obuyambi bwa gavumenti.
Gavumenti z'ensi yonna zikola ku bizibu by'abantu n'eby'enfuna ebiva mu kizibu kya COVID-19.
Ekibiina ky'Eby'enfuna n'Enkulaakulana kitaddewo programu ey'okuwa abantu obubaka obweggulu era obutuukira mu budde ku ngeri ensi z'eyinza okwanukulamu, wamu n'obulagirizi n'amagezi.
Okuva ku nkola ez'okunyweza eby'obulamu n'eby'enfuna by'ensi yonna okutuuka ku ngeri gye bayinza okuvvuunukamu ebikoleddwa mu bitundu eby'enjawulo n'ebiragiro ku ntambula, ekifo kino eky'oku mutimbagano kizingiramu Ekifo ky'Okuteekawo Enkola z'Ebibiina, era kigenderedde okuyamba amawanga okuyigagana n'okusobozesa ensi yonna okwetegeka mu ngeri ey'enjawulo mu kuziyiza ssennyiga omukambwe.
Gavumenti ya China evunaanibwa Amerika, Minisita w'ekitongole kya United Kingdom Michael Gove, ne mutabani wa Pulezidenti wa Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro, olw'engeri gye balabamu ekirwadde kino ekyatandikira mu ssaza ly'e Hubei, mu China.
Abakulira ekibiina kya Communist Party of China (CPC) ku mutendera gw'amasaza balagiddwa ku ngeri gye bakolamu ku kwekalakaasa mu Central China, ekiraga nti si basanyufu n'engeri gavumenti gye ziddukanyizaamu ekirwadde kino mu kitundu kino.
Abamu ku bo bagamba nti kino kyakolebwa okukuuma Xi Jinping, Ssenkulu w'ekibiina ky'Abakomunisiti mu China, okuva ku busungu bw'abantu olw'ekirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe.
Abamu ku bakungu ba China, nga Zhao Lijian, baagaana okukkiriza nti ekirwadde kya coronavirus kyatandikira mu Wuhan, ne bawagira endowooza nti ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kyava mu Amerika oba mu Yitale.
Gavumenti ya Donald Trump ey'omu Amerika yayita coronavirus "akawuka ka China" oba "akawuka ka Wuhan" n'egamba nti "ebikolwa bya China eby'okwekweka byawa amaanyi akawuka kano akafuuse kawuka ka nsi yonna". Ebigambo bino byavumirirwa abamu ng'obuvunaanyizibwa bw'obusosoze era "n'okuggya ebirowoozo ku bulemwa bwa gavumenti ye mu kuddukanya akawuka".
Daily Beast efuna obubaka bwa gavumenti ya Amerika obugamba ku ngeri y'okuwuliziganya era nga butaddewo n'obubaka okuva mu National Security Council, nga bugamba nti "Byonna bikwataganira ku China.
Twayitibwa okugezaako okulangirira obubaka buno mu ngeri yonna esoboka, nga mw'otwalidde n'empapula z'amawulire n'okubeera ku ttivvi". Empapula z'amawulire okuli Politico, Foreign Policy, ne Bloomberg zigamba nti okufuba kwa China okusindika obuyambi mu nsi eziriddwa akawuka ka siriimu kitundu ku ppokopayizaasi y'okuleetawo enkulaakulana mu nsi.
Omukulu w'enteekateeka z'amawanga g'omu Bulaaya, Josep Borrell, yalabula nti waliwo "enkola ya byabufuzi, nga mw'otwalidde okulwanagana olw'obuyinza okuyitira mu kukyamya amazima n'okukozesa 'obwannannyini bw'obugagga.'"
Borrell era agamba nti, "China ekubiriza mu ngeri ey'obukambwe obubaka nti, obutafaanana Amerika, bali ba mukwano beesigika era beesigika".
China era yasabye Amerika okuggyawo ebibonerezo ku Syria, Venezuela ne Iran, era n'ewa obuyambi eri amawanga abiri agasembayo.
Jack Ma eyawaayo masiki 100,000 eri Cuba yaziyizibwa ebibonerezo bya Amerika nga April 3.
Abakulembeze ba Amerika era bavunaanibwa nti baakubye obuyambi bwa Amerika mu mawanga amalala.
Waliwo n'obutabanguko obuli mu nsi endala, gamba nga Germany, Austria, ne Switzerland; n'omu Czech Republic ne Italy.
Ng'oggyeko ekyo, Abatuuki baakwata ebyuma ebikadde eby'okufuuyira empewo ebyali bigendereddwa okugenda mu Spain.
Ku ntandikwa ya Maaki, gavumenti ya Italy yanenya obutakolera bantu ba EU wamu mu Italy nga bakosebwa obulwadde bwa coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, omubaka wa Italy mu European Union, yagamba nti "China yokka ye yakuddamu mu ngeri ey'obwesimbu.
Kya lwatu, kino tekiraga nti tuli bumu mu Bulaaya".
Nga March 22, oluvannyuma lw'okusasulwa essimu okuva eri Katikkiro wa Italy Giuseppe Conte, Pulezidenti wa Russia Vladimir Putin yakubiriza amagye ga Russia okusindika abasawo b'amagye, emmotoka ez'okwekebejja obuwuka, n'ebikozesebwa ebirala mu by'ekisawo mu Italy.
Olupapula lw'amawulire olw'omu Italy oluyitibwa La Stampa lwogera ku "byabufuzi eby'ekitiibwa" ebitaamanyiddwa, nga bigamba nti ebitundu 80 ku buli kikumi eby'obuyambi obwa Russia "tebiriimu oba tebigasa nnyo Italy".
Ensonda zino z'avunaana Russia okubaako ky'ekola mu kulumba "ebibiina by'amawanga eby'enjawulo".
Pulezidenti wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, ne Minisita w'ensonga z'ebweru wa Italy Luigi Di Maio baabuusizza amaaso amawulire ago ne basiima.
Russia era yasindika ennyonyi ezaalimu eby'obujjanjabi mu Amerika.
Omwogezi wa Kremlin Dmitry Peskov yagamba nti "bwe yali awa bannaabwe mu Amerika obuyambi, [Putin] yatandika okulowooza nti singa Amerika esobola okubawa obuyambi, nabo bandisobodde okuddiŋŋana bwe kyandikyuse".
Emizannyo gy'amagye gya NATO "Defender 2020" egitegekeddwa mu Bugirimaani, Poland, n'ensi za Baltic, egisinga obunene okuva ku nkomerero ya Ssematalo ow'Ekyaka, gigenda kutwalibwa ku mutindo mutono.
Kati omuwandiisi wa Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament Kate Hudson yanenya Defender 2020: "Mu kiseera kino eky'obujjanjabi, si bulamu bwa basirikale ba Amerika bokka n'obw'amawanga ga Bulaaya obwenyigirwamu, naye n'obw'abantu b'amawanga mwe bakolera". Gavumenti ya Iran yakosebwa nnyo akawuka kano, nga n'abakiise ba palamenti abasoba mu kkumi na babiri bafunye ekirwadde kino, n'ab'obufuzi abalala kkumi na bataano.
Nga Maaki 14, 2020, Pulezidenti wa Iran Hassan Rouhani yawandiika ebbaluwa eri abakulembeze b'ensi yonna ng'asaba obuyambi era n'agamba nti eggwanga lye lifunye obuzibu mu kulwanyisa ekirwadde kino olw'obutafuna buzibu mu butale bw'ensi yonna ng'ekivuddemu ebibonerezo bya Amerika eri Iran.
Abakugu mu by'ebyobufuzi bagamba nti kino kiyinza okubaako kye kikola ku Donald Trump okuwangula obwakabaka mu 2020 era nti enkolagana y'obufuzi wakati wa Japan ne South Korea eyonoonese olw'obulwadde buno.
South Korea yanenya "obutaba na bwenkanya era obutali bwenkanya mu nkola ya Japan ey'okusiba abantu mu kkomera" oluvannyuma lw'e Japan okulangirira nti buli muntu yenna eyava e South Korea ajja kussibwa mu kkomera okumala wiiki bbiri mu bifo gavumenti by'eragira.
Mu kusooka, abantu mu South Korea baali tebagenda kukkiriziganya ku ngeri Pulezidenti Moon Jae-in gye yandigonjoddemu ekizibu kino.
Abatuuze bangi mu Korea baateekako omukono ku kiwandiiko, nga beegayirira Moon avumirwe, okusinziira ku bigambibwa nti gavumenti yakola ensobi mu ngeri gye yakwatamu ekirwadde, era ne batendereza engeri gye yakwatamu ekirwadde kino.
Abawandiisi abamu baagamba nti ekyo kyandisobozesezza gavumenti okwongera okunyweza obuyinza.
Mu Hungary, palamenti yalondawo okuleka Katikkiro Viktor Orbán okufuga nga yeeyambisa ebiragiro ebitakoma, n'aggyawo palamenti n'okulonda, n'okubonereza abantu abavunaanibwa olw'okulimba ebikwata ku kawuka ka HIV n'engeri gavumenti gye yakwatamu obuzibu.
Obulwadde bwa coronavirus bugambibwa nti bwava ku bbula ly'ebyuma, okuva ku kukozesa ebyuma okw'amaanyi okw'ensi yonna okulwanyisa obulwadde, okunoonya ebintu mu ngeri ey'ekyewuunyo, n'okuddaabiriza emirimu mu makolero n'ebikozesebwa.
Ekitongole kya United States ekirwanyisa endwadde z'obulabe kyalabudde nti waliwo ebbula ly'eddagala n'eby'obujjanjabi olw'okuba abantu beeyongedde okuligula n'olw'okuba nti abatunzi balidde omuliro.
Ebifo ebimu nabyo birina okwekwata olw'okweraliikirira ebiva mu kusula ebintu ebikulu, gamba ng'emmere, amazzi mu kabuyonjo, n'amazzi agali mu biwaawaatiro, ebiviirako ebbula ly'ebintu.
Mu ngeri ey'enjawulo, amakolero g'eby'empuliziganya galabudde ku kukyuka kw'ebiseera eby'okutambuza eby'amasannyalaze.
Okusinziira ku dayirekita w'ekitongole kya WHO, Tedros Adhanom, okwetaaga eby'okwamba okw'omuntu kennyini kweyongedde emirundi 100.
Kino kyayongera ku muwendo gw'ebbeeyi y'eddagala era ne kiviirako okugaziya ebisale by'eddagala okumala emyezi ena oba mukaaga.
Kino kivuddemu n'obutaba na by'okwambala okw'enjawulo okwetooloola ensi yonna, era WHO erabula nti kino kijja kuleetera abalwadde okwongera okwonooneka.
Mu Australia, ekirwadde kino kyawa abaguzi ba daigou omukisa omulala okutunda ebika byabwe mu China.
Kino kyaviirako amata ag'embisi okubula mu maduuka agamu era ne gawerebwa gavumenti ya Australia.
Enkola eyakolebwa China ne Italy okulwanyisa okuterekebwa n'okutundibwa mu ngeri emenya amateeka okw'ebbeeyi, eyambye nnyo mu kuziyiza obwetaavu bw'emmere obwaliwo mu Bulaaya ne mu Amerika.
Ensi ya Northern Italy, erimu ebirime ebingi, tekyafiiriddwako nnyo, naye okusinziira ku bamyuka b'amakolero, ebbeeyi y'ebintu eyinza okulinnya.
Emmere ey'omu tterekero erya bulijjo eyawangaala mu kiseera kino, ne mu kibuga Wuhan, ng'abakulu mu gavumenti y'e China baggyako ennyama y'embizzi mu nkukutu okusobola okukakasa nti abantu bafuna emmere.
Mu Italy, waliwo etteeka erigamba nti abalimi b'emmere balina okuteekawo emmere ey'okwerinda esobole okujjanjabirwa mu mbeera ng'eyo.
Okweyongerayo kw'ebyenfuna mu nsi yonna kuwuliriddwa mu China: okusinziira ku lipoota y'amawulire eyafulumiziddwa nga Maaki 16, ebyenfuna mu China bikoseddwa nnyo mu myezi ebiri egyasooka mu 2020 olw'ebyo gavumenti bye yakola okukomya okusaasaana kw'akawuka, era okutunda mu butale kwagwa 20.5%.
Olw'okuba China y'ensi omukulu mu by'enfuna n'eby'okukola, obulwadde buno bw'ebadde bukulu nnyo mu nsi yonna.
Agathe Demarais ow'ekitongole kya Economist Intelligence Unit agamba nti ebbeeyi y'ebintu ejja kusigala nga y'emu okutuusa ng'ekigendererwa ekituufu kizuuliddwa.
Mu Jjanwali 2020, abawandiisi abamu bateebereza nti enkola y'ebyenfuna mu nsi yonna esobola okusingako n'ey'ekirwadde kya SARS ekyabalukawo mu 2002-2004.
Abakugu mu by'ensimbi ku ssomero lya Washington University mu St. Louis bagamba nti ekizibu kino kiyinza okuleeta obuzibu obuweza obuwumbi 300 mu nsi yonna, era nti kiyinza okutaataaganya ensi okumala emyaka ebiri.
Ekibiina ky'amawanga aguleeta amafuta (OPEC) kigambibwa nti "kyasirikidde" oluvannyuma lw'ebbeeyi y'amafuta okukendeera olw'ebbeeyi y'amafuta okuva mu China.
Ku Lwokubiri 24, ebyenfuna bya bonna mu nsi yonna byakosa nnyo olw'okweyongera kw'omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 ebweru wa China.
Nga 27 omwezi gw'okubiri, olw'okweraliikirira ekirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe, ebitundu by'empapula z'empapula z'Amerika, omuli NASDAQ-100, S&P 500 Index, ne Dow Jones Industrial Average, byafuna okukendeera okw'amaanyi ennyo okuva mu 2008, era Dow n'egwa 1,191 obubonero, era ng'ekyo kye kikyasinga okuba ekiteeso mu kiseera eky'ebinyeebwa by'ensimbi mu 2007-2008.
Ebyapa ebyo byonna bisatu byaggwaako wiiki nga biweddeko ebitundu 10 ku buli kikumi.
Nga Febwali 28, Scope Ratings GmbH yakakasa ekya gavumenti ya China, naye n'ekwata ku ndabika embi.
Empeereza y'obugagga bw'ensi yonna yaddamu okugwa olw'okutya ekirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe, era okugwa okwo okwasinze okubaawo kwaliwo nga Maaki 16.
Abantu bangi balowooza nti embeera y'eby'enfuna eyinza okudda.
Omusuubuzi Mohamed El-Erian asiimye ekikolwa kya bbanka enkulu n'ebitongole ebirala eby'obwannakyewa ebirina obuyinza okuleeta obwavu mu kiseera ekituufu.
Bbanka enkulu z'ensi z'eddira amangu okusinga bwe zaakola mu buzibu bw'ebyenfuna mu 2008.
Ekitundu ky'ebyobulambuzi kye kimu ku bisinga okukosebwa olw'ebibonerezo ku ntambula, okuggalwawo kw'ebifo by'abantu bonna nga mw'otwalidde n'ebifo ebikyalira abantu, n'ebikolwa bya gavumenti eby'okukugira abantu okutambula mu nsi yonna.
Ekyavaamu, ennyonyi nnyingi zaaggyamu ennyonyi zaabwe olw'obwetaavu obutono, omwali British Airways, China Eastern Airlines, ne Qantas, ate ennyonyi endala ez'omu kitundu ekya Bungereza Flybe ne zigwa.
Ebizibu ebivudde mu ntambula y'amatooke biri ku kigero ekitabangawo.
Ebitundu by'eggaali y'omukka n'amaato nabyo byaggalwa.
Obulwadde buno bw'egatta ku Chunyun, ekiseera eky'ennyonyi ekikulu ekikwataganyizibwa n'okuwummula kw'omwaka omuggya ogw'omu China.
Emikolo egisinga obungi egikwataganyizibwa n'abantu abangi gyaggyiddwawo gavumenti ya China n'ebitundu, omuli n'embaga y'omwaka omupya ogwa Lunar, era n'amakampuni ag'obwannannyini gaggalawo ku ggoolo zaabwe n'ebifo ebikyaza abantu, gamba nga Hong Kong Disneyland ne Shanghai Disneyland.
Embaga nnyingi ez'omwaka omupya ogw'omu China n'ebifo eby'obulambuzi byaggalwawo okusobola okuziyiza abantu okukuŋŋaana awamu, nga mw'otwalidde ekibuga ekiziikibwa e Beijing n'ebifo eby'obuwangwa eby'omu China.
Mu bitundu 24 ku 31 ebya China, ebibuga n'ebitundu, ab'obuyinza bongeddeyo ennaku z'okuwummula ez'omwaka omupya okutuuka nga Febwali 10 era ne balagira emirimu egisinga obutaddamu kutandika okutuusa nga Febwali 10.
Ensi eno ebaleetera ebitundu 80 ku buli kikumi eby'enkulaakulana y'ensi eno n'ebitundu 90 ku buli kikumi eby'envuma.
Hong Kong yassaawo obuvvulu bw'endwadde ez'obukaba ku kigero ekisingawo era yalangirira embeera ey'obwewaggu, n'aggala amasomero okutuusa mu Maaki, era n'okuggyawo embaga z'omwaka omupya.
Okukyala mu katale mu Bulaaya ne Latin America kukendeera ebitundu 40 ku buli kikumi.
Abasuubuzi mu Amerika ey'ebukiikakkono n'Abasiraamu bafiiriddwa ebitundu 50 ku buli 60 ku buli 100.
Kino era kyaviirako ebbeeyi y'abatambuze ku bigere mu bifo omuli amaduuka okutambula okukendeera ebitundu 33-43% mu March bw'ogigeraageranya ne February.
Abaddukanya ebifo by'amaduuka okwetooloola ensi bataddewo enkola endala, gamba ng'okulongoosa obuyonjo, okussa amasannyalaze mu bifo by'abaguzi, n'okukomya emikolo. Okusinziira ku kitebe kya UN Economic Commission for Latin America, ekirwadde kino kiyinza okuviirako abantu abali mu bwavu obw'amaanyi mu Amerika ey'omu Latin okweyongera okuva ku bukadde 14 okutuuka ku bukadde 22 bw'ogeraageranya n'abantu abaaliwo nga tewali bulwadde.
Mu Jjanwali ne Febwali 2020, mu kiseera ekirwadde kya Wuhan we kyabeerera ku ntikko, abantu obukadde 5 mu China baafiirwa emirimu gyabwe.
Mu mwezi gwa March 2020, abantu abasukka mu bukadde 10 mu Amerika baafiirwa emirimu gyabwe ne basaba gavumenti okubayamba.
Okusinziira ku kubalirira kwa Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis, ekirwadde kya coronavirus kiyinza okufiiriza abantu obukadde 47 emirimu mu Amerika ate ebbula ly'emirimu liyinza okutuuka ku bitundu 32 ku 100.
Mu kitundu eky'okubiri eky'omwezi gwa Maaki, abakozi obukadde 4 mu Bufalansa baasaba obuyambi bw'ekiseera obwa bulijjo, ate abakozi obukadde 1 mu Bungereza baasaba enteekateeka y'okukozesa ssente z'ensi yonna.
Enteekateeka z'ebbanja ly'abakozi ab'ekiseera ekitono mu Bugirimaani zaatwalibwa mu Bufalansa ne Bungereza.
Okwetooloola ensi, ebitongole ebikola eby'obutonde n'eby'obusika bikoseddwa nnyo ekirwadde kino, ekireeseewo enkola y'ebitongole n'abantu kinnoomu, abakola n'abateesalirawo.
Ebibiina by'ebyobuwangwa n'ebitone by'abantu bigezaako okutuukiriza obuvunaanyizibwa bwabyo (obuvunaanyizibwa bwabyo busasanyizibwa bantu bonna) okuleeta eby'obugagga by'abantu eri abantu, okukuuma abakozi n'abantu abali mu mbeera ennungi, n'okuwagira abayimbi bwe kiba kisoboka.
Mu Maaki 2020, okwetooloola ensi yonna era ku mitendera egy'enjawulo, amadiini, amakuŋŋaaniro g'ebitabo, ebifo eby'emizannyo, n'ebitongole ebirala eby'obuwangwa byaggalwa, era n'ebiragisi, emizannyo, n'ebikolwa by'obuwangwa byasengulwa oba byasengulwa.
Mu kwanukula, okufuba okw'amaanyi kukoleddwa okuwa obuweereza obulala okuyita mu bifo ebya digito. Obuzibu obulala obuzze buva ku bulwadde buno obweyongera amangu, kwe kukomya okusinza, emizannyo eminene, n'emikolo emirala egy'abantu, gamba ng'embaga z'ennyimba n'amazina, enkuŋŋaana z'ebikugu, n'emikolo gy'okwambala.
Ate era, olw'okuba abantu bangi mu nsi yonna bagenze mu kibuga ekyo, abantu bangi nnyo mu nsi eyo baava mu kibuga ekyo.
Amadiini mangi gakubiriza Abakristaayo abakaddiye okusigala mu maka gaabwe era ne beewala okujja mu Misa ku Ssande; amakanisa agamu gakola ku leediyo, ku ntambi z'amasinzizo ez'oku mutimbagano oba ku ttivi, ate amalala gakola ku mmotoka.
Ng'Ekkanisa n'ekkanisa bya Rooma bishop's (Abasumba b'Ekikatuliki) bizingiddwa era nga n'olusuku lwa Peetero luli bwereere, ebibiina by'eddiini ebirala nabyo byaggyawo enkuŋŋaana era ne bikugira abantu okukuŋŋaana mu masinzizo, amasinagogi, yeekaalu, n'amadiini.
Minisitule y'ebyobulamu mu Iran yalangirira okuggyawo okusaba kw'Olwokutaano mu bitundu ebiriddwako obulwadde buno era amasinzizo ne gaggalwa, ng'ate Saudi Arabia eremesa abagwira n'abantu okuyingira mu bifo ebitukuvu e Mecca ne Medina.
Ekirwadde kino kye kyaleeseewo okusaasaana okw'amaanyi ennyo mu byafaayo by'emizannyo mu nsi yonna okuva mu Ssematalo II.
Emizannyo mingi giggaddwa oba gisibiddwa, omuli UEFA Champions League 2019-2020, Premier League 2019-2020, UEFA Euro 2020, NBA 2019-2020, ne NHL 2019-20
Olukaya luno lw'ebikolobero lwaleetawo akabi mu mpaka z'Emikono eza 2020 ezaali zaategekebwa okutandika mu nkomerero ya Jjulaayi; Akakiiko k'Emikono Ak'ensi Yonna kakalangirira nga 24 Maaki nti emikolo gino "gijja kuddamu okuteekebwako nga wayise mu 2020, naye nga tegijja kusukka mu 2021".
Kino kiviiriddeko bangi okuva ku mizanyo gy'okuzannya omupiira ne bagenda ku mizannyo gya Internet, era n'okufuna abazannyi abawerako.
Amaterere agasinga obungi nga Broadway nago gayimirizaayo ebikolwa byago byonna.
Abayimbi bano banoonyereza ku ngeri endala ez'okweyongera okufulumya n'okugabana emirimu gyabwe ku mutimbagano gw'oku mutimbagano, gamba nga okuyita ku mutimbagano gw'oku mutimbagano oba okuteekawo "emikolo" ku mutimbagano gw'oku mutimbagano, basobole okuleeta, okusaasaanya n'okulangirira emirimu gyabwe.
Ebifaananyi bingi ku mikutu gya Internet ku kirwadde kya coronavirus bicaase nnyo ku mutimbagano nga bangi baliko bye bakozesa okusaaga n'okusekerera mu kiseera kino eky'obutamanya.
Okuva COVID-19 lweyatandika, wabaddewo okweyongerayongera mu kusosola, obusosoze n'obusosoze eri abantu ab'obuzaale obuva mu China ne East Asia, n'abantu okuva mu bitundu ebirwadde ebirwadde bino we bikoseddwa mu Bulaaya, Amerika, n'ensi endala.
Okutya, obukyayi, n'obukyayi birabikira mu nsi nnyingi, naddala mu Bulaaya, Asiya ow'Ebuvanjuba, Amerika ow'omu Bukiika Kkono, ne mu Asiya ne mu Pacific.
Alipoota okuva mu February (ng'ababalwadde abasinga bakyali mu China) yalaga endowooza z'obwenkaniddevu mu bibiina ebitali bimu okwetooloola ensi nti Abasiayina basaanidde okufuna akawuka oba okufuna kye bagamba nti kye kivaamu.
