Okufuga akabi ak'obutonde bw'omulimu ku COVID-19
Okuziyiza akabi ka COVID-19 mu kifo ky'okukola kwe kukozesa enkola y'obukuumi n'obulamu mu bifo by'okukozesa okusobola okuziyiza akabi okusobola okwewala ekirwadde kya coronavirus ekya 2019 (COVID-19).
Okuziyiza akabi mu bifo by'okolera kisinziira ku kifo n'emirimu gy'okola, okusinziira ku kuddamu akabi akali mu by'okutuusa akawuka ku bantu, obulwadde bw'olimu mu kitundu, n'ensonga eziviirako abakozi okukwatibwa obulwadde bwa COVID-19.
Okusinziira ku U.S. Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), emirimu egirina obubenje obutonotono gy'egyo egirina emikwano mitono n'abantu abalala; emirimu gino gyesigibwa n'ebikolwa eby'okutangira obulwadde, omuli okunaaba engalo, okukubiriza abakozi okubeera mu ddwaliro, empisa y'okussa empewo, n'okulongoosa n'okusaanya obujjanjabi mu kifo ky'omulimu.
Emirimu egiriko akabi ak'obutereevu mwe muli n'emirimu egikwatagana ennyo n'abantu abatamanyi oba abateeberezebwa okuba ne COVID-19 naye nga bayinza okuba nga bafunye obulwadde buno olw'okuyisa ekirwadde mu bantu oba olw'entambula y'ensi yonna.
Ekibinja kino kizingiramu abakozi abalina enkolagana n'abantu abalala gamba nga mu masomero, mu bifo omuli abantu abangi, n'ebitundutundu eby'amaduuka.
Okwewala akabi mu bantu bano, ng'oggyeko ebikolwa ebisookerwako eby'okwewala okusaasaana kw'obulwadde, mulimu okufuuyisa empewo ng'okozesa ebizigo by'empewo eby'obuyambi, eby'okukuuma okukama, n'okuteekawo eby'okwekweka nga waliwo omuntu alina COVID-19.
Abakozi mu bifo ebirimu abantu abalina COVID-19 mu bifo ebirimu abantu abafa, beetaaga okulabirirwa mu ddwaaliro ly'omusawo, era nga kino kivaako okwongera okusaasaanya ennyo singa abakozi be bakola ku bantu abalina COVID-19 oba be batwala ebifaananyi oba be bakwata ku bantu abalina COVID-19.
Obuyambi buno obw'obulabe eri abakozi buzingiramu obuyambi bw'enkola, gamba nga, ekisenge ekirimu empewo ezirimu obuzibu, n'eby'okwerinda ebikozesebwa ku mulimu.
Okubalukawo kwa COVID-19 kuyinza okubaako kye kukola ku bifo by'omulimu.
Omukozi ayinza okugaana okukola olw'obulwadde, olw'obwetaavu bw'okulabirira abalala, oba olw'okutya okuteebwa.
Enkola z'obusuubuzi ziyinza okukyuka, okusinziira ku ngeri y'ebintu ebisabibwa n'engeri y'okubikoleramu (ng'okusuubula mu biseera eby'eddembe, okuyita mu ntambula, oba okuyita mu ntambula).
Mu nkomerero, okusindikibwa kw'ebintu okuva mu bitundu ebirina COVID-19 kuyinza okutaataaganyizibwa. Okwewala okwetegekera n'okwerinda kw'endwadde ez'akawuka biyinza okukozesebwa okutaasa.
Enteekateeka eno eraga obuzibu obuli mu bifo eby'enjawulo n'emirimu egy'enjawulo, omuli ebitundu by'oyinza okubeeramu, embeera z'awaka ne mu kitundu, n'obutabanguko obuli mu bakozi kinnoomu, gamba ng'obukadde oba obulwadde.
Enteekateeka era ebalaga obukuumi obwetaagibwa okuziyiza obuzibu obwo n'enteekateeka ey'obwezo mu mbeera yonna eyinza okubalukawo olw'ekirwadde kino.
Okwewala endwadde ez'akawuka n'okweteekateeka mu ngeri ey'obukuumi biyinza okuba nga bikwatagana n'ebiragiro by'eggwanga oba eby'ebitongole ebikola ku nsonga ez'enjawulo.
Ebigendererwa by'okumalawo obulwadde buno bizingiramu okukendeeza ku kusasaana kw'obulwadde mu bakozi, okukuuma abantu abali mu kabi k'endwadde ez'amaanyi, okukuuma emirimu gy'emirimu gy'amakampuni, n'okutangira obuzibu obuyinza okujjawo ku bantu abalala abali mu by'okwerinda.
Obukalu bw'obulwadde mu kitundu bizinensi mwe biri birina kinene kye bikola ku ngeri y'okumalawo obulwadde.
Obukwakkulizo bw'okugezesa obuzibu (Hazard control hierarchy) ye nkola ekozesebwa ennyo mu bukuumi n'obulamu mu mirimu okutegeka obuzibu okusinziira ku ngeri gye buganyula.
Obuzibu bwa COVID-19 bwe butayinza kuggyibwawo, okuziyiza okusingira ddala kuba kujja kuba kutereeza ebintu, nga kuddirirwa okuziyiza ebikolwa, ate okusembayo nga kw'ekuuma omuntu.
