Gavuna wa New York Andrew Cuomo yalangirira nti okunoonyereza kwa chloroquine ne hydrochlorokuine mu New York kutandika nga 24 March. Nga 28 March, FDA yakkiriza okukozesa hydroxychloroquine sulfate ne chloroquine phosphate okusinziira ku Emergency Use Authorization (EUA).
