Mu mwezi gwa April, abakugu mu CEPI baategeezezza nti mu 2020 waakubeerawo okunoonyereza n'okukulaakulanya mu nkola ey'obujjanjabi ku nninga 10 ez'enjawulo okusobola okufuna eddagala erigema okulwanyisa COVID-19.
Ebiruubirirwa ebikulu eby'okuteeka mu nkola eby'okwerinda mu kutendekebwa okw'omulundi ogusooka, mwe muli:
nucleic acid (DNA ne RNA) (abazimba Phase I n'omulwadde w'eddagala: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
ekikonge ky'akawuka (oyo akola eddagala erya Phase I n'eriryegereka: CanSino Biologics, ekikonge kya adenovirus type 5)
Nga bannasayansi ba CEPI bwe baategeezezza mu Apuli, ab'obuyinza 115 be baali batandise okubateekateeka, 78 be baakakasa nti baali bakola (79, okusinziira ku Milken Institute), ate abalala 37 be baali balaze, naye nga tewali kalonda yenna eri mu lujjudde (nga kigambibwa nti baali bateekateeka oba baali bateekateeka).
Ebigezo bya Phase I-II bisuubirwa mu ngeri ey'obukuumi n'obutabaako bulwadde, nga buli kiseera bikola mu ngeri ya placebo, era nga buli kifo kijjako eddagala erina okuba nga ly'esobola okutaasa omuntu.
Okukemebwa okw'ekigero III okutera okukolebwa ku bantu abangi, nga mw'otwalidde n'ekibinja ky'okulaba, era nga kigezesa obukakafu bw'omuddwaaliro ku bulwadde, nga bwe kulabirirwa n'ebivaako ng'omulwadde afunye ekirwadde.
Ku balwadde 79 abali mu nkola ey'okwekulaakulanya (baakakasibwa mu ntandikwa ya April 2020), 74 ku bo tebannaba kugezesebwa mu bantu (bakyali mu kunoonyereza kwa "preclinical").
