Mu April 2020, waaliwo okunoonyereza okw'emirundi esatu nga kukyagenda mu maaso.
Ebigezo musanvu byagezesa eddagala erikkirizibwa okujjanjaba omusujja, nga mw'otwalidde n'ebiri ku hydroxychloroquine oba chloroquine.
Eddagala erya antiviral eryaggya lirina okunoonyereza okungi mu China, nga waliwo enkambi z'okugezesa z'eddagala lya remdesivir mu mitendera 3 mu nsi ez'enjawulo nga balina okuteesa ku nkomerero ya Apuli.
Mu April 2020, okunoonyereza ku nkulaakulana y'eddagala ly'omulwadde wa COVID-19 n'eddagala eririko byatandika. Eddagala eririko erirwanyisa ekirwadde likola ku bulwadde bwa COVID-19, omuli remdesivir, chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir, ne lopinavir/ritonavir nga ekoleddwa ne beta interferon.
Mu Maaki 2020, waaliwo obujulizi obwasooka obulaga nti remdesivir ya mugaso.
Obulwadde buno bwabalukawo mu balwadde abaalina eddagala eriyitibwa remdesivir mu ddwaaliro ly'eddwaliro.
Ebisale by'eddagala mu Amerika, China ne Italy bikyali mu kutendekebwa. Chloroquine, eddagala eryali likozesebwa edda okujjanjaba omusujja, lyanoonyezebwa mu China mu February 2020, n'ebivaamu okusooka.
Kyokka, waliwo okukaabira okwekenneenya okukolebwa bannaffe.
Abakungu b'ebyobulamu mu Korea ne China bakubiriza okukozesa chloroquine.
Kyokka, ekitongole ekiyitibwa Wuhan Institute of Virology, wadde nga kikubiriza abantu okufuna gramu emu eya sukaali buli lunaku, kyagamba nti okugafuna emirundi ebiri ky'ekibi era kiyinza n'okutta omuntu.
Nga 28 Ogwokusatu, 2020, FDA yakkiriza okukozesa eddagala lya hydroxychloroquine ne chloroquine mu ngeri ey'obw'obuvunaanyizibwa bw'abasawo abajjanjaba abalwadde ba COVID-19.
Ebimanyiddwa mu ntandikwa biraga nti eddagala eddene erya ribavirin lyetaagisa okuziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu mubiri.
Nitazoksanide yakubirizibwa okwongera okukozesebwa mu vivo oluvannyuma lw'okulaga nti esobola okuziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu bukendeevu. Okunoonyereza kwalaga nti ekirungo kya protein ekisooka mu bukadde (priming) eky'omubiri (protin) ekirimu ekitibwa transmembrane protease 2 (TMPRSS2) kyetaagisa nnyo SARS-CoV-2 okuyingira mu mubiri okuyita mu kukwatagana ne ACE2 receptors.
Okunoonyereza ku chlorokuyini ne hydroxychloroquine nga kw'otadde azithromycin yalina obukwakkulizo bungi obwalemesezza abasawo okukozesa enzijanjaba eno nga tebinnaba kwekenneenyezebwa. Oseltamivir teziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu bizinensi era terina kifo kye kimanyiddwa mu bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19.
Obuzibu bw'omuzira gw'ensiri busobola okubaawo mu COVID-19 ey'amaanyi.
Waliwo obujulizi obulaga nti hydroxychloroquine eyinza okuba n'ebirungo eby'okulwanyisa cytokine. Tocilizumab yateekebwa mu mpisa z'abasawo ba National Health Commission of China oluvannyuma lw'okunoonyereza okutono okwakolebwa.
Eddagala lino lirina okukolebwa mu kutendekebwa okw'omulundi ogwokubiri mu Italy oluvannyuma lw'okulaga ebivaamu ebirungi mu bantu abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Nga kigattiddwa n'okugezesa omusaayi okwa serumu ya ferritin okuzuula ekigezo kya cytokine, eddagala lino ligendereddwamu okulwanyisa ekigezo kya cytokine, ekikakkanyizibwa okuba nga kye kiviirako okufa kw'abantu abamu abakosebwa.
Mu 2017, eddagala eriyitibwa interleukin-6 receptor antagonist lyasiimibwa FDA okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu bantu ku ngeri gye bayinza okujjanjabamu endwadde ya steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome nga bakozesa eddagala eriyitibwa CAR T cell therapy.
N'okutuusa kati, tewali bujulizi bwa lukusa na bulondoola obulaga nti tocilizumab ddagala ddamu eri CRS.
Okusaasaanya obuwuka obuggya obwekubisiba mu mubiri bw'abantu abawonye COVID-19 eri abo ababufuna mu ngeri y'okumuziyiza nga tebannamuggya mu mubiri, kuterebwako.
Enteekateeka eno yakeberwa ku SARS naye n'evaamu ebibala ebitaweesa ssuubi.
Okuziyiza akawuka ka siriimu y'engeri ey'okukozesa eddagala erirwanyisa endwadde erirwanyisa SARS-CoV-2.
